1
00:00:16,492 --> 00:00:20,262
(Christmas filled with excitement)

2
00:00:20,732 --> 00:00:23,202
(The kids met each other for the first time.)

3
00:00:24,032 --> 00:00:26,172
(And the First Impression Selection)

4
00:00:28,042 --> 00:00:29,471
(Thank you for saying I lightened the mood!)

5
00:00:29,472 --> 00:00:30,511
(Let's get along well!)

6
00:00:30,512 --> 00:00:32,112
(I hope we become friends.)

7
00:00:32,472 --> 00:00:35,212
(Choi Yu Bin chose Yoon Hoo.)

8
00:00:35,482 --> 00:00:37,912
(Park Si Woo chose Yoon Hoo.)

9
00:00:38,352 --> 00:00:45,292
(Yoon Hoo received 2 votes in the First Impression Selection.)

10
00:00:45,422 --> 00:00:47,122
- I'll try my best. - Okay.

11
00:00:47,962 --> 00:00:49,961
(Let's make it together.)

12
00:00:49,962 --> 00:00:51,832
You and I have similar taste.

13
00:00:52,062 --> 00:00:53,802
(We'll click really well.)

14
00:00:53,862 --> 00:00:55,702
- We hit it off well. - Do we?

15
00:00:56,132 --> 00:00:57,601
(But the latecomer arrived soon after.)

16
00:00:57,602 --> 00:00:58,732
- What? - Finally.

17
00:00:59,202 --> 00:01:01,271
(A good-looking latecomer appeared.)

18
00:01:01,272 --> 00:01:03,572
- Gosh. - Oh, my.

19
00:01:04,012 --> 00:01:05,942
(I feel bad for Yoon Hoo.)

20
00:01:06,912 --> 00:01:10,552
(The daughters' hearts are racing,)

21
00:01:11,112 --> 00:01:15,322
(and the sons are on guard.)

22
00:01:16,582 --> 00:01:20,892
(How will the latecomer impact the kids?)

23
00:01:21,162 --> 00:01:24,031
A new male resident appeared out of nowhere.

24
00:01:24,032 --> 00:01:25,831
He turned things upside down...

25
00:01:25,832 --> 00:01:28,531
the minute he joined the kids.

26
00:01:28,532 --> 00:01:32,402
This kid also has a dad.

27
00:01:32,732 --> 00:01:34,372
- Of course. - Yes.

28
00:01:34,602 --> 00:01:35,901
Of course he has a dad.

29
00:01:35,902 --> 00:01:38,211
And you all know the dad very well.

30
00:01:38,212 --> 00:01:39,311
- It could be a mom. - True.

31
00:01:39,312 --> 00:01:41,381
- We might know her well. - There won't be another mom.

32
00:01:41,382 --> 00:01:42,841
- What? - There won't be another mom.

33
00:01:42,842 --> 00:01:44,012
Be happy with me.

34
00:01:45,912 --> 00:01:48,051
- No more moms. - Let's hope you're the only mom.

35
00:01:48,052 --> 00:01:49,122
Right.

36
00:01:49,182 --> 00:01:51,351
- Is he an athlete? - An athlete?

37
00:01:51,352 --> 00:01:52,491
- For some reason. - Since he's tall?

38
00:01:52,492 --> 00:01:53,492
That's plausible.

39
00:01:53,492 --> 00:01:54,492
(While there are many guesses,)

40
00:01:55,292 --> 00:01:57,231
(the latecomer's dad enters shyly.)

41
00:01:57,232 --> 00:01:58,592
It's Tae Woong!

42
00:02:00,132 --> 00:02:01,132
(The parents greet him happily.)

43
00:02:01,133 --> 00:02:02,662
- It's been a while. - Have you been well?

44
00:02:02,802 --> 00:02:04,072
- Tae Woong. - Hi.

45
00:02:05,432 --> 00:02:07,672
No wonder the son was a looker.

46
00:02:08,202 --> 00:02:10,711
The new resident's dad...

47
00:02:10,712 --> 00:02:13,112
is actor You Tae Woong.

48
00:02:15,012 --> 00:02:17,712
(A good-looker with defined features)

49
00:02:18,782 --> 00:02:22,382
(The actor who left a lasting impression in "The Wild Days")

50
00:02:22,822 --> 00:02:27,661
(Still handsome despite all the years)

51
00:02:27,662 --> 00:02:30,361
The good-looking dad has a good-looking son.

52
00:02:30,362 --> 00:02:31,461
- Exactly. - Right?

53
00:02:31,462 --> 00:02:33,861
- The son is more handsome. - He got it from Tae Woong.

54
00:02:33,862 --> 00:02:35,102
- Totally. - Right?

55
00:02:35,832 --> 00:02:37,471
How tall is he?

56
00:02:37,472 --> 00:02:38,532
Over 190cm, right?

57
00:02:39,072 --> 00:02:40,401
He's 197cm.

58
00:02:40,402 --> 00:02:41,472
- What? - Gosh.

59
00:02:42,002 --> 00:02:43,472
- That's really tall. - He's 197cm?

60
00:02:43,972 --> 00:02:45,342
He's as tall as Michael Jordan.

61
00:02:46,742 --> 00:02:47,912
That's too tall.

62
00:02:48,342 --> 00:02:50,381
Shouldn't the residents have a height limit?

63
00:02:50,382 --> 00:02:51,412
I know, right?

64
00:02:52,152 --> 00:02:53,252
Just look at the height difference.

65
00:02:55,152 --> 00:02:56,791
- You're really tall. - Yes.

66
00:02:56,792 --> 00:02:57,792
(Bewildered by the tall latecomer)

67
00:02:58,222 --> 00:03:01,421
- What's your name? - I'm You Hee Dong.

68
00:03:01,422 --> 00:03:02,991
- Hee Dong. - Hee Dong.

69
00:03:02,992 --> 00:03:04,032
That's right.

70
00:03:05,432 --> 00:03:09,201
(Handsome ever since he was a kid)

71
00:03:09,202 --> 00:03:11,001
Gosh, what a looker.

72
00:03:11,002 --> 00:03:12,372
He hasn't changed.

73
00:03:13,572 --> 00:03:14,841
How charming.

74
00:03:14,842 --> 00:03:17,671
(Grew up looking just like his dad)

75
00:03:17,672 --> 00:03:20,482
- He's more handsome than his dad. - The air he gives off, right?

76
00:03:22,942 --> 00:03:27,052
I'm a physical education major at Korea University.

77
00:03:28,322 --> 00:03:30,052
I'm on the baseball team.

78
00:03:30,622 --> 00:03:32,622
I'm a pitcher.

79
00:03:33,222 --> 00:03:35,521
- So he does baseball. - He's even in the baseball team.

80
00:03:35,522 --> 00:03:36,561
(Even on the baseball team?)

81
00:03:36,562 --> 00:03:38,431
- He's a pitcher? - A pitcher.

82
00:03:38,432 --> 00:03:40,232
- Remember Koo Ja Wook? - Koo Ja Wook of Samsung.

83
00:03:40,602 --> 00:03:41,661
He's like Koo Ja Wook...

84
00:03:41,662 --> 00:03:42,701
- of the Lions. - Totally.

85
00:03:42,702 --> 00:03:44,032
The next-generation Koo Ja Wook.

86
00:03:51,942 --> 00:03:53,912
My strength would be...

87
00:03:54,912 --> 00:03:58,711
my sharp curveballs, which batters have a hard time hitting.

88
00:03:58,712 --> 00:03:59,712
(His height is his weapon.)

89
00:03:59,782 --> 00:04:02,851
I won the Excellent Pitcher Award for the first half of the year...

90
00:04:02,852 --> 00:04:05,122
in the weekend league during high school senior year...

91
00:04:05,222 --> 00:04:08,291
and have won it multiple times.

92
00:04:08,292 --> 00:04:10,492
(Hee Dong pours his passion into baseball.)

93
00:04:10,932 --> 00:04:13,492
(Do you often hear that you're handsome?)

94
00:04:14,132 --> 00:04:15,162
Honestly,

95
00:04:15,632 --> 00:04:16,762
I do.

96
00:04:20,172 --> 00:04:23,971
When I went out to the hallway to switch classrooms in high school,

97
00:04:23,972 --> 00:04:26,142
other students came rushing out to see me.

98
00:04:28,582 --> 00:04:29,782
Saying it myself...

99
00:04:30,182 --> 00:04:31,551
He's got everything.

100
00:04:31,552 --> 00:04:33,212
(Saying it myself is a bit...)

101
00:04:34,082 --> 00:04:36,621
Since I keep playing baseball,

102
00:04:36,622 --> 00:04:38,852
there hasn't been much time to date.

103
00:04:39,722 --> 00:04:43,392
Experiencing something new is very exciting.

104
00:04:43,692 --> 00:04:46,762
I'd love to take photos with my girlfriend like my friends do...

105
00:04:47,102 --> 00:04:50,402
and have a lovey-dovey relationship.

106
00:04:51,702 --> 00:04:53,542
- He's got it all. - So young.

107
00:04:53,942 --> 00:04:59,412
(Episode 2: A Restless Night)

108
00:05:00,072 --> 00:05:01,581
- Nice to meet you. - Nice to meet you.

109
00:05:01,582 --> 00:05:02,882
Nice to meet you.

110
00:05:06,212 --> 00:05:09,352
- Why do you have a flower with you? - I know, right?

111
00:05:14,762 --> 00:05:16,061
He brought a flower with him.

112
00:05:16,062 --> 00:05:18,392
(Everyone is curious.)

113
00:05:27,402 --> 00:05:28,741
Hold on a minute.

114
00:05:28,742 --> 00:05:31,811
(The new resident is to give the flower...)

115
00:05:31,812 --> 00:05:34,882
(to the girl with the best first impression.)

116
00:05:38,282 --> 00:05:39,911
Without talking to each other?

117
00:05:39,912 --> 00:05:40,921
Without chitchatting?

118
00:05:40,922 --> 00:05:42,751
He's choosing while everyone is there?

119
00:05:42,752 --> 00:05:45,122
- Oh, dear. I feel bad for him. - That's a bit...

120
00:05:45,892 --> 00:05:48,121
(Yoon Hoo, the popular guy with 2 First Impression votes,)

121
00:05:48,122 --> 00:05:50,392
(has checked the text message.)

122
00:05:50,862 --> 00:05:51,862
Interesting.

123
00:05:54,202 --> 00:05:57,802
(Choosing the one who made the best first impression openly)

124
00:05:58,072 --> 00:06:01,742
I have my hopes up a little.

125
00:06:05,512 --> 00:06:08,042
To be frank, just a tiny bit.

126
00:06:11,382 --> 00:06:14,582
My hopes went up by 0.1 percent. Just 0.1 percent.

127
00:06:15,482 --> 00:06:17,852
Yu Bin is trying to look cute.

128
00:06:18,652 --> 00:06:20,822
Yu Bin is trying to look cute.

129
00:06:21,062 --> 00:06:22,121
That's not a face...

130
00:06:22,122 --> 00:06:23,591
- she makes at home. - Yu Bin is...

131
00:06:23,592 --> 00:06:24,761
I guess you're not familiar with that face.

132
00:06:24,762 --> 00:06:26,762
- It's new to me. - A new expression.

133
00:06:27,302 --> 00:06:29,732
- A face you haven't seen at home. - No.

134
00:06:30,702 --> 00:06:34,942
(While everyone is nervous)

135
00:06:35,442 --> 00:06:36,971
Did everyone read the text message?

136
00:06:36,972 --> 00:06:38,112
- Yes. - Yes.

137
00:06:42,012 --> 00:06:43,111
Here.

138
00:06:43,112 --> 00:06:47,381
(For the First Impression Selection, Hee Dong chooses...)

139
00:06:47,382 --> 00:06:48,482
Thank you.

140
00:06:49,882 --> 00:06:54,222
(Si Woo.)

141
00:06:54,362 --> 00:06:55,461
The girl in front of him.

142
00:06:55,462 --> 00:06:56,462
(Si Woo was chosen by three guys.)

143
00:06:56,463 --> 00:06:59,291
- Gosh. - Goodness, Si Woo.

144
00:06:59,292 --> 00:07:01,002
Hee Dong is very straightforward.

145
00:07:01,502 --> 00:07:02,601
- Right? - She must have made...

146
00:07:02,602 --> 00:07:03,972
a nice first impression.

147
00:07:06,002 --> 00:07:07,002
Oh, dear.

148
00:07:15,142 --> 00:07:18,081
(Why did you choose Si Woo?)

149
00:07:18,082 --> 00:07:20,482
First of all,

150
00:07:21,552 --> 00:07:23,151
she sat right across from me.

151
00:07:23,152 --> 00:07:24,852
We made eye contact several times.

152
00:07:26,622 --> 00:07:31,162
Her bright smile really did something to me.

153
00:07:31,692 --> 00:07:35,362
She stood out the moment I looked at everyone.

154
00:07:38,372 --> 00:07:39,802
It made me happy.

155
00:07:40,772 --> 00:07:42,672
Yes, it did.

156
00:07:43,342 --> 00:07:46,772
No girl would hate receiving flowers.

157
00:07:47,582 --> 00:07:50,652
(Did it boost your interest in Hee Dong?)

158
00:07:52,782 --> 00:07:54,552
Yes, of course.

159
00:07:58,292 --> 00:08:02,922
(Meanwhile, Yu Bin was watching the whole situation.)

160
00:08:03,192 --> 00:08:04,262
It was a bummer.

161
00:08:05,692 --> 00:08:09,331
Either way, his looks were my ideal type,

162
00:08:09,332 --> 00:08:11,172
which got me interested in him.

163
00:08:11,332 --> 00:08:15,071
I'm sure I'll get a chance to talk to Hee Dong...

164
00:08:15,072 --> 00:08:16,202
next time.

165
00:08:18,372 --> 00:08:19,642
Thank you.

166
00:08:22,342 --> 00:08:23,482
Oh, dear.

167
00:08:24,082 --> 00:08:26,411
- How does it feel? - Sit over here.

168
00:08:26,412 --> 00:08:27,422
No, don't.

169
00:08:27,552 --> 00:08:28,921
- I'll switch seats with you. - No, it's okay.

170
00:08:28,922 --> 00:08:30,651
- Really. - No, you should sit over there.

171
00:08:30,652 --> 00:08:31,822
(Yu Bin changes seats.)

172
00:08:32,992 --> 00:08:34,362
Is she switching seats?

173
00:08:34,392 --> 00:08:35,761
Maybe Yu Bin wants to see him from the front...

174
00:08:35,762 --> 00:08:37,021
by switching seats with Si Woo.

175
00:08:37,022 --> 00:08:38,262
I know, right?

176
00:08:42,232 --> 00:08:47,442
(Hee Dong and Si Woo sit closely, thanks to Yu Bin.)

177
00:08:47,602 --> 00:08:49,942
(Glancing)

178
00:08:58,412 --> 00:08:59,951
Did everyone have dinner?

179
00:08:59,952 --> 00:09:01,521
- Yes. - Yes, what about you?

180
00:09:01,522 --> 00:09:03,681
- I only had a little. - Is that so?

181
00:09:03,682 --> 00:09:05,421
Is there anything you can't eat?

182
00:09:05,422 --> 00:09:06,852
No, I eat anything and everything.

183
00:09:08,122 --> 00:09:10,862
What kind of food do you like the most?

184
00:09:10,962 --> 00:09:12,361
- Anything with rice, - Rice.

185
00:09:12,362 --> 00:09:13,762
like bibimbap and rice bowls.

186
00:09:14,202 --> 00:09:15,331
What about kimchi fried rice?

187
00:09:15,332 --> 00:09:16,432
I like it.

188
00:09:17,902 --> 00:09:20,772
I'll make it for you in a bit.

189
00:09:21,072 --> 00:09:23,801
(Yu Bin makes a sudden move.)

190
00:09:23,802 --> 00:09:26,272
- Hee Dong... - Is it Hee Dong?

191
00:09:28,312 --> 00:09:30,011
Yoon Hoo got two votes...

192
00:09:30,012 --> 00:09:31,681
- in the First Impression Selection. - Right.

193
00:09:31,682 --> 00:09:34,682
Those were from Yu Bin and Si Woo.

194
00:09:35,222 --> 00:09:38,192
- The two seem to waver. - Exactly.

195
00:09:38,422 --> 00:09:40,661
Yoon Hoo is...

196
00:09:40,662 --> 00:09:42,661
- Will he be okay? - Didn't you hear him earlier?

197
00:09:42,662 --> 00:09:44,562
- What did he say again? - "Interesting."

198
00:09:45,492 --> 00:09:46,831
"Things are interesting."

199
00:09:46,832 --> 00:09:49,161
- He's enjoying it. - Right.

200
00:09:49,162 --> 00:09:50,162
(Trying to stay calm)

201
00:09:50,362 --> 00:09:52,432
The latecomer is a wild one.

202
00:09:53,402 --> 00:09:56,301
He's too wild. Come on, Tae Woong.

203
00:09:56,302 --> 00:09:57,811
A big, wild latecomer.

204
00:09:57,812 --> 00:09:58,841
(Everyone is nervous about the big, wild latecomer.)

205
00:09:58,842 --> 00:09:59,942
We've got a wild one.

206
00:10:01,042 --> 00:10:03,482
Can we unpack our things now?

207
00:10:03,582 --> 00:10:05,082
- Yes, shall we? - Let's go unpack.

208
00:10:08,122 --> 00:10:09,321
(Si Woo and Eun Byul's room)

209
00:10:09,322 --> 00:10:11,392
Oh, my. You received the flowers.

210
00:10:11,952 --> 00:10:14,362
- You got a Christmas gift. - Right.

211
00:10:15,522 --> 00:10:16,592
Gosh.

212
00:10:18,832 --> 00:10:21,661
By the way, he's like 190cm tall.

213
00:10:21,662 --> 00:10:23,331
- Right? - I've never seen someone...

214
00:10:23,332 --> 00:10:24,401
as tall as him before.

215
00:10:24,402 --> 00:10:27,442
- Like 190cm? - Maybe 196cm.

216
00:10:28,102 --> 00:10:29,201
- Almost 200cm? - That's 200cm.

217
00:10:29,202 --> 00:10:30,342
Exactly.

218
00:10:30,872 --> 00:10:33,112
- I have to look up at him. - It was a surprise.

219
00:10:35,342 --> 00:10:36,811
- Earlier, - Yes?

220
00:10:36,812 --> 00:10:39,351
- when we sent the text message, - Yes.

221
00:10:39,352 --> 00:10:41,551
- it was out of the blue. - Right?

222
00:10:41,552 --> 00:10:43,151
We know nothing about each other.

223
00:10:43,152 --> 00:10:44,522
- Exactly. - I just...

224
00:10:45,492 --> 00:10:48,162
Did your first impression change after?

225
00:10:48,622 --> 00:10:50,892
(Interested)

226
00:10:51,062 --> 00:10:54,402
- No, it didn't. - Did it not?

227
00:10:54,732 --> 00:10:56,101
That's how you should be.

228
00:10:56,102 --> 00:10:57,672
- Of course. - Stay consistent.

229
00:10:58,772 --> 00:11:00,601
- What about you? - Mine has changed.

230
00:11:00,602 --> 00:11:01,672
- Really? - Yes.

231
00:11:02,642 --> 00:11:03,941
- What? - It changed.

232
00:11:03,942 --> 00:11:05,371
Si Woo's first impression has changed.

233
00:11:05,372 --> 00:11:07,581
- My dear son. - She said Hoo was cute.

234
00:11:07,582 --> 00:11:09,342
- Si Woo did. - It changed.

235
00:11:10,242 --> 00:11:12,752
(Yoon Hoo and Jae Hyuk's room)

236
00:11:13,182 --> 00:11:15,181
- He's super tall. I'm jealous. - Same here.

237
00:11:15,182 --> 00:11:16,222
(Even they are talking about the latecomer.)

238
00:11:17,182 --> 00:11:18,792
Hee Dong is such a looker.

239
00:11:19,892 --> 00:11:21,521
Setting aside how handsome he is,

240
00:11:21,522 --> 00:11:22,962
- it's his height. - I know.

241
00:11:24,232 --> 00:11:25,532
Can't he give some of it to me?

242
00:11:26,462 --> 00:11:28,531
Genetically speaking, I lucked out.

243
00:11:28,532 --> 00:11:29,761
- That's totally true. - Yes.

244
00:11:29,762 --> 00:11:30,872
He's taller than his dad.

245
00:11:31,902 --> 00:11:33,832
I'll just blame my dad.

246
00:11:34,502 --> 00:11:35,502
(Dumbfounded)

247
00:11:35,503 --> 00:11:37,312
Jae Hyuk is holding it against his dad.

248
00:11:37,572 --> 00:11:40,742
He blames everything he lacks on me.

249
00:11:44,082 --> 00:11:45,251
(Jae Seung and Hee Dong's room)

250
00:11:45,252 --> 00:11:47,251
This is the room we'll use together.

251
00:11:47,252 --> 00:11:48,522
(Jae Seung and Hee Dong's room)

252
00:11:50,722 --> 00:11:52,052
Are you good at making friends?

253
00:11:52,292 --> 00:11:55,091
I get along with guys really quickly,

254
00:11:55,092 --> 00:11:57,492
- Not with girls? - but I find it hard with girls.

255
00:11:59,292 --> 00:12:03,962
I always hang out with my baseball teammates,

256
00:12:04,202 --> 00:12:08,172
so I'm not the type to approach girls with confidence.

257
00:12:08,272 --> 00:12:10,472
I wait for them to approach me.

258
00:12:11,112 --> 00:12:12,172
I see.

259
00:12:12,612 --> 00:12:13,842
They'd approach him for sure.

260
00:12:13,972 --> 00:12:15,281
What a surprise.

261
00:12:15,282 --> 00:12:17,681
He'll need some time with the girls.

262
00:12:17,682 --> 00:12:18,751
- It'll be hard. - Yes.

263
00:12:18,752 --> 00:12:20,552
He doesn't know much about girls' hearts.

264
00:12:22,722 --> 00:12:24,821
(Hee Dong, who finds girls difficult,)

265
00:12:24,822 --> 00:12:26,192
Excuse me.

266
00:12:26,522 --> 00:12:27,961
- You'll have something, right? - Yes.

267
00:12:27,962 --> 00:12:31,591
(only follows Jae Seung around.)

268
00:12:31,592 --> 00:12:33,891
Go hang out with the girls,

269
00:12:33,892 --> 00:12:35,932
not only with Jae Seung. Come on.

270
00:12:37,132 --> 00:12:38,932
- Do you work out? - Yes.

271
00:12:39,772 --> 00:12:40,971
I have to, even if just a little.

272
00:12:40,972 --> 00:12:43,042
Everyone here works out.

273
00:12:46,972 --> 00:12:48,841
(Yu Bin walks over to the two guys.)

274
00:12:48,842 --> 00:12:50,212
Are you done unpacking?

275
00:12:50,282 --> 00:12:51,312
- Yes. - I see.

276
00:12:52,212 --> 00:12:54,152
(Turning)

277
00:12:54,382 --> 00:12:55,922
Do you have a workout routine?

278
00:12:57,322 --> 00:12:59,552
(Choi Yu Bin, Choi Jae Won's daughter)

279
00:13:00,992 --> 00:13:02,792
What kind of workout do you like the most?

280
00:13:05,592 --> 00:13:06,892
Just this and that.

281
00:13:07,862 --> 00:13:11,572
(The conversation doesn't continue smoothly.)

282
00:13:13,572 --> 00:13:15,072
Would you like to play board games?

283
00:13:15,372 --> 00:13:17,241
(You Hee Dong, You Tae Woong's son)

284
00:13:17,242 --> 00:13:18,312
Right now?

285
00:13:19,942 --> 00:13:21,281
- How about it? - Okay.

286
00:13:21,282 --> 00:13:22,781
- You know how to play it, right? - Yes.

287
00:13:22,782 --> 00:13:23,812
Good.

288
00:13:25,752 --> 00:13:27,952
Luckily, there was a game for three.

289
00:13:29,622 --> 00:13:32,792
(With Yu Bin's help, the guys and girls finally hang out together.)

290
00:13:33,622 --> 00:13:35,091
You guys play games, right?

291
00:13:35,092 --> 00:13:37,562
I'm not forcing you, am I?

292
00:13:38,362 --> 00:13:39,791
I play board games on my phone.

293
00:13:39,792 --> 00:13:40,902
For real? Me too.

294
00:13:42,432 --> 00:13:44,232
We might grow close after playing this game.

295
00:13:44,832 --> 00:13:46,071
(Laughing)

296
00:13:46,072 --> 00:13:47,132
Maybe not.

297
00:13:49,972 --> 00:13:53,542
(The residents gather in the living room one at a time.)

298
00:13:54,042 --> 00:13:57,142
(Hee Dong looks a lot more relaxed now.)

299
00:14:01,182 --> 00:14:02,222
Hi.

300
00:14:03,482 --> 00:14:04,992
I didn't know you were playing a game.

301
00:14:06,252 --> 00:14:08,222
- Are you three playing? - Yes.

302
00:14:09,222 --> 00:14:11,632
(Focused solely on the game)

303
00:14:12,432 --> 00:14:14,532
(Park Si Woo, Park Nam Jung's daughter)

304
00:14:14,762 --> 00:14:16,202
Time out.

305
00:14:21,072 --> 00:14:22,742
She's being conscious of them a little.

306
00:14:23,272 --> 00:14:24,971
- Of course. - "When will it end?"

307
00:14:24,972 --> 00:14:26,142
- Something like that. - Right.

308
00:14:26,812 --> 00:14:28,782
The end of the board game.

309
00:14:29,412 --> 00:14:30,642
The end.

310
00:14:31,482 --> 00:14:32,652
What should we do?

311
00:14:34,682 --> 00:14:36,722
- Since he just arrived, - Yes?

312
00:14:36,782 --> 00:14:38,551
- how about playing cards? - The one from earlier?

313
00:14:38,552 --> 00:14:40,352
- Yes, Balance Game. - I'm in.

314
00:14:41,522 --> 00:14:43,191
You give the question...

315
00:14:43,192 --> 00:14:45,762
to the person you want the answer from.

316
00:14:46,362 --> 00:14:48,161
- Gosh. - Oh, this looks interesting.

317
00:14:48,162 --> 00:14:49,861
- Goodness. - Isn't it Truth or Dare?

318
00:14:49,862 --> 00:14:51,631
- It's a sort of Truth or Dare, - I see.

319
00:14:51,632 --> 00:14:54,601
but you get to ask the question to the person you want.

320
00:14:54,602 --> 00:14:56,141
- You don't go in turns. - Okay.

321
00:14:56,142 --> 00:14:57,941
Once you draw a card and read it,

322
00:14:57,942 --> 00:15:00,312
you pass it to the person you want the answer from.

323
00:15:00,612 --> 00:15:02,141
- That's right. - You get to know their feelings.

324
00:15:02,142 --> 00:15:03,681
- Exactly. - I see.

325
00:15:03,682 --> 00:15:04,682
Balance Game.

326
00:15:05,952 --> 00:15:07,111
(Starting off with Jae Hyuk)

327
00:15:07,112 --> 00:15:09,682
"I prefer to say 'I love you...'"

328
00:15:09,752 --> 00:15:11,351
"as many times as possible..."

329
00:15:11,352 --> 00:15:12,421
"or only when..."

330
00:15:12,422 --> 00:15:15,222
"I really feel the love."

331
00:15:17,162 --> 00:15:19,591
- Goodness. - Either say it countless times.

332
00:15:19,592 --> 00:15:21,931
I'm sure he'll give it to Si Woo.

333
00:15:21,932 --> 00:15:23,362
- He sure will. - Right?

334
00:15:28,472 --> 00:15:31,472
(Jae Hyuk hands the card to Si Woo, his First Impression choice.)

335
00:15:32,912 --> 00:15:34,841
- He's steadfast. - I told you.

336
00:15:34,842 --> 00:15:36,311
- How competitive. - He lives up...

337
00:15:36,312 --> 00:15:38,181
- to expectations. - Totally.

338
00:15:38,182 --> 00:15:39,552
(Jae Hyuk is still curious about Si Woo.)

339
00:15:40,112 --> 00:15:42,921
I prefer saying it...

340
00:15:42,922 --> 00:15:45,992
only when I really feel the love.

341
00:15:52,232 --> 00:15:55,032
"I want my partner to do this when things are tough."

342
00:15:55,062 --> 00:15:57,462
"Ask me questions to figure it out."

343
00:15:57,832 --> 00:16:00,772
"Figure out how I'm feeling without me having to explain."

344
00:16:01,302 --> 00:16:02,601
- Okay. - This time...

345
00:16:02,602 --> 00:16:04,971
- Who will this card go to? - Let's see.

346
00:16:04,972 --> 00:16:06,071
- It matters. - Right.

347
00:16:06,072 --> 00:16:08,342
- Who will get the card? - Who will get it?

348
00:16:09,712 --> 00:16:12,111
(Thinking)

349
00:16:12,112 --> 00:16:14,782
She should give it to Yoon Hoo.

350
00:16:14,852 --> 00:16:17,722
- Hee Dong. - I bet she'll give it to Hee Dong.

351
00:16:18,952 --> 00:16:20,992
Okay, Coach Shin Tae Yong.

352
00:16:22,962 --> 00:16:26,531
(The person to receive Si Woo's card is...)

353
00:16:26,532 --> 00:16:30,661
(Hee Dong.)

354
00:16:30,662 --> 00:16:32,772
- It's Hee Dong. - Hee Dong right away.

355
00:16:33,172 --> 00:16:35,472
- Poor Jae Hyuk. - How honest of her.

356
00:16:35,802 --> 00:16:37,241
This is frustrating.

357
00:16:37,242 --> 00:16:39,371
There's no reason for her not to give it to Hee Dong,

358
00:16:39,372 --> 00:16:41,382
- who gave her flowers. - True.

359
00:16:42,782 --> 00:16:46,481
(Si Woo passed the card to Hee Dong, maybe because of the flowers.)

360
00:16:46,482 --> 00:16:49,322
Yoon Hoo is being forgotten.

361
00:16:51,422 --> 00:16:53,622
I'm most likely the latter.

362
00:16:55,962 --> 00:16:57,731
"I appreciate my partner more..."

363
00:16:57,732 --> 00:16:58,991
"when they make me laugh..."

364
00:16:58,992 --> 00:17:01,062
"or when they laugh when I'm being funny."

365
00:17:02,732 --> 00:17:06,732
(Who will Hee Dong give the card to?)

366
00:17:08,702 --> 00:17:11,241
(The person to receive Hee Dong's card is...)

367
00:17:11,242 --> 00:17:15,341
(Yu Bin.)

368
00:17:15,342 --> 00:17:17,751
- It went to Yu Bin. - But why?

369
00:17:17,752 --> 00:17:19,911
- They played a game together. - He gave it to Yu Bin.

370
00:17:19,912 --> 00:17:21,782
- True. - But the flowers went to Si Woo.

371
00:17:24,392 --> 00:17:26,922
- Oh, dear. - Look at Si Woo.

372
00:17:27,092 --> 00:17:28,392
Si Woo is sulking.

373
00:17:29,362 --> 00:17:31,092
When they laugh when I'm being funny.

374
00:17:31,192 --> 00:17:34,462
That makes me happier.

375
00:17:36,362 --> 00:17:41,142
(The atmosphere has become strange.)

376
00:17:42,742 --> 00:17:44,671
"When in a long-distance relationship,"

377
00:17:44,672 --> 00:17:46,672
"I'm more moved..."

378
00:17:46,842 --> 00:17:49,542
"when my partner can't visit often but says how much they miss me..."

379
00:17:49,742 --> 00:17:52,652
"or when my partner visits without saying how much they miss me."

380
00:17:53,312 --> 00:17:56,482
(Thinking)

381
00:17:56,952 --> 00:18:00,922
(Who does Yu Bin want to know about?)

382
00:18:03,422 --> 00:18:06,291
(Yu Bin's card...)

383
00:18:06,292 --> 00:18:08,432
(goes to Hee Dong.)

384
00:18:09,762 --> 00:18:12,371
Yu Bin, why did you change your mind from Hoo?

385
00:18:12,372 --> 00:18:13,831
Goodness, it went to Hee Dong.

386
00:18:13,832 --> 00:18:15,971
- This is bad. - Hoo versus Hee Dong.

387
00:18:15,972 --> 00:18:17,342
This is nerve-racking.

388
00:18:18,042 --> 00:18:20,871
(Even Yu Bin, after Si Woo, passed the card to Hee Dong.)

389
00:18:20,872 --> 00:18:26,652
(Even Yu Bin, after Si Woo, passed the card to Hee Dong.)

390
00:18:27,152 --> 00:18:29,481
I like it when my partner puts it into action.

391
00:18:29,482 --> 00:18:31,092
- A doer. - Same here.

392
00:18:39,592 --> 00:18:42,262
- Is this a question for a couple? - It's a good one.

393
00:18:42,532 --> 00:18:44,732
"Fried chicken should be plain or seasoned."

394
00:18:47,632 --> 00:18:48,802
It's important.

395
00:18:48,872 --> 00:18:51,372
True, the difference in taste.

396
00:18:54,382 --> 00:18:55,442
I...

397
00:18:55,542 --> 00:18:56,742
- Me? - Yes.

398
00:18:57,342 --> 00:19:01,522
(Hee Dong passes the second card to Si Woo.)

399
00:19:02,352 --> 00:19:03,822
She looks bright again.

400
00:19:04,452 --> 00:19:05,891
- Si Woo... - Really.

401
00:19:05,892 --> 00:19:08,221
Her expression changes when she gets and doesn't get the card.

402
00:19:08,222 --> 00:19:10,291
- Right? - She can't hide her expression.

403
00:19:10,292 --> 00:19:11,762
- No. - Nobody can.

404
00:19:11,932 --> 00:19:13,431
My expression changes...

405
00:19:13,432 --> 00:19:14,962
- with Si Woo's. - Of course.

406
00:19:15,162 --> 00:19:16,162
I...

407
00:19:16,332 --> 00:19:17,361
- Me? - Yes.

408
00:19:17,362 --> 00:19:18,632
(When Hee Dong's card goes to Si Woo)

409
00:19:20,902 --> 00:19:22,372
Right in front of her eyes...

410
00:19:22,542 --> 00:19:24,441
The card was passed on right in front of her eyes.

411
00:19:24,442 --> 00:19:27,612
- What was that? - Her expression was so honest.

412
00:19:29,242 --> 00:19:30,242
Oh, no.

413
00:19:30,243 --> 00:19:32,311
They'll probably get into a fight.

414
00:19:32,312 --> 00:19:33,682
- Totally. - The daughters will.

415
00:19:37,722 --> 00:19:39,452
I like plain fried chicken.

416
00:19:43,422 --> 00:19:44,462
What about you?

417
00:19:45,962 --> 00:19:46,992
Both are good.

418
00:19:48,702 --> 00:19:50,302
- Half and half? - Half and half.

419
00:19:50,562 --> 00:19:52,672
Was half and half even one of the options?

420
00:19:57,972 --> 00:20:00,012
I asked Yu Bin a question,

421
00:20:00,142 --> 00:20:01,882
and then Si Woo one.

422
00:20:02,782 --> 00:20:05,082
It's the first day, so I don't know that much about them.

423
00:20:05,352 --> 00:20:06,952
I want to get to know both of them.

424
00:20:09,782 --> 00:20:10,852
That's good.

425
00:20:10,952 --> 00:20:12,121
- You need to figure them out. - He's right.

426
00:20:12,122 --> 00:20:14,251
At first, Hee Dong gave...

427
00:20:14,252 --> 00:20:16,292
the bouquet of flowers to Si Woo.

428
00:20:16,522 --> 00:20:18,361
- Then, they played games together. - With Yu Bin.

429
00:20:18,362 --> 00:20:19,731
He played games with Yu Bin.

430
00:20:19,732 --> 00:20:22,162
- Yu Bin is very... - She takes the initiative.

431
00:20:22,202 --> 00:20:23,431
We've all seen it,

432
00:20:23,432 --> 00:20:27,071
but she's been flirting with them.

433
00:20:27,072 --> 00:20:28,701
- Flirting? - She's very proactive.

434
00:20:28,702 --> 00:20:31,002
- It's all part of the process. - It is.

435
00:20:31,142 --> 00:20:32,871
She might be strongly drawn to one guy after this.

436
00:20:32,872 --> 00:20:33,912
Right.

437
00:20:34,042 --> 00:20:36,181
There must be a lot on her mind.

438
00:20:36,182 --> 00:20:37,182
Yes.

439
00:20:37,183 --> 00:20:38,682
(Who will Hee Dong choose in the end?)

440
00:20:39,282 --> 00:20:42,081
- You haven't had dinner, right? - No. Should we eat first?

441
00:20:42,082 --> 00:20:44,422
(The children start cooking for Hee Dong, who's hungry.)

442
00:20:45,192 --> 00:20:46,492
Can you cook?

443
00:20:47,152 --> 00:20:49,121
- I can cook rabokki. - Wait.

444
00:20:49,122 --> 00:20:50,791
Do you like rabokki? Should we cook that?

445
00:20:50,792 --> 00:20:52,662
- Yes, let's make rabokki. - Just rabokki?

446
00:20:52,992 --> 00:20:54,191
Without any meat?

447
00:20:54,192 --> 00:20:55,432
I'll grill some meat.

448
00:20:56,302 --> 00:20:58,972
I think we put too many fish cakes.

449
00:20:59,172 --> 00:21:00,302
Excuse me.

450
00:21:01,602 --> 00:21:03,102
There are too many fish cakes.

451
00:21:03,302 --> 00:21:05,742
Sorry about that.

452
00:21:05,812 --> 00:21:07,572
- You like fish cakes, right? - I do.

453
00:21:08,782 --> 00:21:10,181
I put a lot on purpose...

454
00:21:10,182 --> 00:21:11,882
because I knew you'd like them.

455
00:21:13,652 --> 00:21:16,582
(Grinning)

456
00:21:16,882 --> 00:21:18,822
- Do you like it soggy? - I do.

457
00:21:19,292 --> 00:21:20,752
(Approaching)

458
00:21:23,062 --> 00:21:24,862
He says yes to everything.

459
00:21:25,192 --> 00:21:26,762
- He's a yes-man. - He is.

460
00:21:27,092 --> 00:21:28,502
Do you like your noodles firm?

461
00:21:28,562 --> 00:21:29,731
- I do. - She can't join them.

462
00:21:29,732 --> 00:21:30,802
Really?

463
00:21:32,272 --> 00:21:36,101
They were getting along really well.

464
00:21:36,102 --> 00:21:38,111
Though he chose me at first,

465
00:21:38,112 --> 00:21:41,171
I thought he could be more interested...

466
00:21:41,172 --> 00:21:43,982
in Yu Bin.

467
00:21:45,152 --> 00:21:46,611
Enjoy your food.

468
00:21:46,612 --> 00:21:47,851
(Their dinner begins amidst a subtle tension.)

469
00:21:47,852 --> 00:21:50,321
- Thank you for the food. - Thank you for the food.

470
00:21:50,322 --> 00:21:51,522
- Thank you for the food. - Thank you for the food.

471
00:21:52,322 --> 00:21:53,322
You can eat first.

472
00:21:53,323 --> 00:21:55,562
(Hee Dong)

473
00:21:56,892 --> 00:21:59,231
(Yu Bin openly cared about Hee Dong.)

474
00:21:59,232 --> 00:22:01,231
- She's offering him first. - She's totally into him!

475
00:22:01,232 --> 00:22:03,532
- She is. - No one can eat first.

476
00:22:03,632 --> 00:22:04,971
She's leading the dinner...

477
00:22:04,972 --> 00:22:06,831
- at the head of the table. - Did Yu Bin make...

478
00:22:06,832 --> 00:22:09,201
- a gesture at Hee Dong? - Yes.

479
00:22:09,202 --> 00:22:10,802
Are there no rules against that?

480
00:22:12,342 --> 00:22:15,011
- That's a little... - Si Woo is losing right now.

481
00:22:15,012 --> 00:22:18,151
I mean, there should be some basic rules.

482
00:22:18,152 --> 00:22:20,082
Right. She doesn't want anybody else to eat first.

483
00:22:20,812 --> 00:22:21,922
What do you think?

484
00:22:23,482 --> 00:22:24,552
It's good.

485
00:22:26,992 --> 00:22:28,692
(Relieved)

486
00:22:35,062 --> 00:22:36,402
Come to think of it,

487
00:22:36,632 --> 00:22:40,502
my specialty wasn't kimchi fried rice.

488
00:22:41,342 --> 00:22:43,471
- It was egg fried rice. - Egg fried rice.

489
00:22:43,472 --> 00:22:45,672
- I'm good at egg fried rice. - With soy sauce and eggs.

490
00:22:45,872 --> 00:22:48,642
But I only use eggs and rice.

491
00:22:50,642 --> 00:22:52,582
- Tomorrow's breakfast? - Tomorrow's breakfast? Okay.

492
00:22:54,082 --> 00:22:55,822
- The meat is good, isn't it? - It is.

493
00:22:58,752 --> 00:23:00,121
What else should I ask?

494
00:23:00,122 --> 00:23:01,322
(Glancing)

495
00:23:03,362 --> 00:23:04,491
How do you feel?

496
00:23:04,492 --> 00:23:06,932
Do you think you're settling in well?

497
00:23:08,532 --> 00:23:09,762
- Not yet. - Not yet?

498
00:23:15,442 --> 00:23:17,042
Have you ever drunk until you blacked out?

499
00:23:17,342 --> 00:23:18,372
Well...

500
00:23:18,772 --> 00:23:20,312
- Oh, once. - Once?

501
00:23:22,942 --> 00:23:25,551
Alcohol tastes bad, doesn't it?

502
00:23:25,552 --> 00:23:27,381
- It tastes so bad. - Right.

503
00:23:27,382 --> 00:23:29,382
- Why are you drinking it, then? - For the vibe.

504
00:23:29,682 --> 00:23:30,752
For the vibe.

505
00:23:31,522 --> 00:23:32,551
That's true.

506
00:23:32,552 --> 00:23:35,962
I feel like I'll feel even lonelier if I drink alone.

507
00:23:36,192 --> 00:23:38,532
You come to enjoy that loneliness.

508
00:23:39,932 --> 00:23:41,962
Jae Seung is being too pretentious.

509
00:23:42,402 --> 00:23:44,562
I can't really see the resemblance with his dad.

510
00:23:45,132 --> 00:23:46,632
He takes after her mom.

511
00:23:47,372 --> 00:23:48,372
Jae Seung.

512
00:23:48,802 --> 00:23:51,302
When you're in bitter love,

513
00:23:51,912 --> 00:23:54,112
and you go home after a fight with your boyfriend,

514
00:23:54,372 --> 00:23:57,041
listen to "It's Not Love If It Hurts Too Much."

515
00:23:57,042 --> 00:23:58,852
That will make you cry so hard.

516
00:24:00,912 --> 00:24:02,322
You should listen to it.

517
00:24:03,022 --> 00:24:06,321
Songs these days can never recreate that old-fashioned vibe.

518
00:24:06,322 --> 00:24:07,352
Really?

519
00:24:08,692 --> 00:24:09,961
I wonder why people drink.

520
00:24:09,962 --> 00:24:12,532
(And one person is interested in Jae Seung.)

521
00:24:13,662 --> 00:24:16,361
(It's Eun Byul, who picked him for the First Impression Selection.)

522
00:24:16,362 --> 00:24:17,602
Who's your favorite singer?

523
00:24:20,272 --> 00:24:21,572
Do you like Kim Kwang Seok's songs?

524
00:24:22,072 --> 00:24:23,441
I don't know any of his songs.

525
00:24:23,442 --> 00:24:25,142
(She quietly gets up.)

526
00:24:26,972 --> 00:24:30,312
I couldn't exactly jump in.

527
00:24:30,682 --> 00:24:32,182
It looked like...

528
00:24:32,712 --> 00:24:35,721
Jae Seung and Si Woo have been talking a lot.

529
00:24:35,722 --> 00:24:37,652
They seemed close.

530
00:24:38,392 --> 00:24:42,192
And I'm not the type to approach a guy first,

531
00:24:42,622 --> 00:24:45,462
so I couldn't really express my interest...

532
00:24:45,862 --> 00:24:47,992
or go up to talk to him.

533
00:24:49,362 --> 00:24:51,972
Eun Byul is also interested in Jae Seung.

534
00:24:52,172 --> 00:24:53,971
It's awkward to sit there...

535
00:24:53,972 --> 00:24:55,502
- when the other two are talking. - Exactly.

536
00:24:56,342 --> 00:24:58,471
She's very considerate.

537
00:24:58,472 --> 00:24:59,972
She seems sincere.

538
00:25:01,312 --> 00:25:06,582
(Meanwhile, Jae Hyuk started cooking meat.)

539
00:25:11,182 --> 00:25:14,052
(When he washed dishes with Si Woo,)

540
00:25:14,822 --> 00:25:18,432
(he promised to cook meat for her.)

541
00:25:20,162 --> 00:25:22,131
So, he's doing it for Si Woo.

542
00:25:22,132 --> 00:25:24,332
- He must be. - To show her.

543
00:25:24,802 --> 00:25:28,102
I listen to songs like "Sunflower" and "Flower."

544
00:25:28,572 --> 00:25:30,601
That's unexpected.

545
00:25:30,602 --> 00:25:31,671
(Peeking)

546
00:25:31,672 --> 00:25:33,572
I don't like getting too immersed.

547
00:25:36,742 --> 00:25:37,812
You drink pretty well.

548
00:25:38,042 --> 00:25:41,982
But when I'm sober...

549
00:25:43,282 --> 00:25:44,651
Wait, what was that look?

550
00:25:44,652 --> 00:25:45,921
- Si Woo! - He's a little mad.

551
00:25:45,922 --> 00:25:47,691
Si Woo, you should have noticed him cooking meat.

552
00:25:47,692 --> 00:25:48,762
Right.

553
00:25:50,322 --> 00:25:52,832
I thought it was my chance to show off my charm,

554
00:25:53,032 --> 00:25:54,492
so I cooked meat.

555
00:25:55,232 --> 00:25:59,472
But I saw how much she was talking to Jae Seung.

556
00:26:00,202 --> 00:26:01,572
It bothered me.

557
00:26:03,842 --> 00:26:06,111
(The meat is all cooked.)

558
00:26:06,112 --> 00:26:07,212
Awesome.

559
00:26:08,112 --> 00:26:10,681
- He cut it really well. - It's presented so nicely.

560
00:26:10,682 --> 00:26:12,182
I just cut it with a knife.

561
00:26:13,012 --> 00:26:15,252
(Nom)

562
00:26:16,122 --> 00:26:17,152
What do you think?

563
00:26:17,752 --> 00:26:18,851
It's good.

564
00:26:18,852 --> 00:26:20,192
(Moaning)

565
00:26:20,952 --> 00:26:24,392
(Everyone's enjoying it, but Si Woo isn't eating it.)

566
00:26:27,292 --> 00:26:28,432
You're not hungry, are you?

567
00:26:29,362 --> 00:26:30,561
- Did you eat a lot? - Yes.

568
00:26:30,562 --> 00:26:32,772
I'm not that hungry.

569
00:26:34,002 --> 00:26:37,341
(Feeling bad)

570
00:26:37,342 --> 00:26:39,941
Si Woo, he cooked it for you.

571
00:26:39,942 --> 00:26:40,942
Right.

572
00:26:41,782 --> 00:26:43,381
Try to open up.

573
00:26:43,382 --> 00:26:45,612
(Si Woo, open up to him.)

574
00:26:47,582 --> 00:26:51,082
(Oblivious to their mismatched feelings,)

575
00:26:52,222 --> 00:26:57,292
(the first night wears on.)

576
00:26:58,022 --> 00:26:59,832
(A text message arrives at that moment.)

577
00:27:03,362 --> 00:27:04,501
Wait, what?

578
00:27:04,502 --> 00:27:08,002
(The Attraction Selection will begin now.)

579
00:27:08,972 --> 00:27:10,171
(Send a text with the name of the person...)

580
00:27:10,172 --> 00:27:11,371
(who made your heart flutter today.)

581
00:27:11,372 --> 00:27:13,741
The one who made my heart flutter right now?

582
00:27:13,742 --> 00:27:14,742
I guess so.

583
00:27:14,743 --> 00:27:16,281
It's time for the Attraction Selection.

584
00:27:16,282 --> 00:27:17,341
- What's this? - Attraction?

585
00:27:17,342 --> 00:27:18,481
All right.

586
00:27:18,482 --> 00:27:20,181
This is getting direct.

587
00:27:20,182 --> 00:27:22,121
It's different from the First Impression Selection.

588
00:27:22,122 --> 00:27:24,621
- They've felt things now. - Things have progressed.

589
00:27:24,622 --> 00:27:25,722
Exactly.

590
00:27:26,622 --> 00:27:28,721
(What changes did Hee Dong bring?)

591
00:27:28,722 --> 00:27:31,732
(What changes did Hee Dong bring?)

592
00:27:34,362 --> 00:27:36,332
You're looking around too much.

593
00:27:37,802 --> 00:27:40,232
(To the person that made their heart flutter,)

594
00:27:41,172 --> 00:27:46,142
(they send a text with their feelings.)

595
00:27:48,682 --> 00:27:50,542
You guys seem very cautious.

596
00:27:50,942 --> 00:27:52,111
I suddenly feel...

597
00:27:52,112 --> 00:27:53,152
(Smiling)

598
00:27:54,152 --> 00:27:55,181
I sent mine.

599
00:27:55,182 --> 00:27:58,592
(They've all replied to the text message.)

600
00:27:59,492 --> 00:28:05,432
(Their feelings will be delivered one by one.)

601
00:28:07,662 --> 00:28:09,232
(Nervous)

602
00:28:10,202 --> 00:28:14,832
(Who will get the first message?)

603
00:28:18,372 --> 00:28:19,942
- We have a text. - Who got it?

604
00:28:20,112 --> 00:28:21,242
Who got the text?

605
00:28:23,242 --> 00:28:28,421
(Let's go to a scenic spot and take pictures together.)

606
00:28:28,422 --> 00:28:29,721
- Jae Seung! - Jae Seung?

607
00:28:29,722 --> 00:28:31,151
- Jae Seung. - "Let's go to a scenic spot..."

608
00:28:31,152 --> 00:28:32,322
"and take pictures together."

609
00:28:32,392 --> 00:28:33,891
(Who sent this message?)

610
00:28:33,892 --> 00:28:35,092
- I wonder who it is. - Who is it?

611
00:28:36,692 --> 00:28:39,162
You're on a date...

612
00:28:39,762 --> 00:28:42,562
and your partner asks, "Who did you pick last night?"

613
00:28:44,132 --> 00:28:45,972
I can see that happening.

614
00:28:46,372 --> 00:28:48,172
In the Attraction Selection,

615
00:28:48,802 --> 00:28:50,941
the message read,

616
00:28:50,942 --> 00:28:53,471
"Let's go to a scenic spot and take pictures together."

617
00:28:53,472 --> 00:28:55,482
I'm guessing it's Si Woo.

618
00:28:56,782 --> 00:28:59,152
(In the living room after they moved in)

619
00:28:59,382 --> 00:29:01,581
I also like listening to music,

620
00:29:01,582 --> 00:29:03,782
watching movies, and taking pictures.

621
00:29:04,122 --> 00:29:05,491
I also like taking pictures.

622
00:29:05,492 --> 00:29:06,852
- Do you? - Yes.

623
00:29:07,022 --> 00:29:08,321
I thought so.

624
00:29:08,322 --> 00:29:09,691
Do you also take portraits?

625
00:29:09,692 --> 00:29:10,792
Not really?

626
00:29:10,962 --> 00:29:12,431
- Just landscapes? - Yes, landscapes.

627
00:29:12,432 --> 00:29:13,662
(Si Woo and Jae Seung had similar interests.)

628
00:29:14,862 --> 00:29:19,632
(Is the message from Si Woo as he assumes?)

629
00:29:20,602 --> 00:29:23,172
(Peeking)

630
00:29:23,542 --> 00:29:24,872
I sent it...

631
00:29:25,472 --> 00:29:27,942
to Jae Seung.

632
00:29:29,712 --> 00:29:31,912
He mentioned landscapes...

633
00:29:32,882 --> 00:29:35,352
and said that he liked taking photos.

634
00:29:36,022 --> 00:29:38,281
(The one who remembered Jae Seung's photography...)

635
00:29:38,282 --> 00:29:41,822
(was Eun Byul.)

636
00:29:43,722 --> 00:29:45,062
I wrote that I also liked scenic spots...

637
00:29:45,362 --> 00:29:49,502
and that we should go and take pictures together.

638
00:29:51,902 --> 00:29:53,571
It was Eun Byul.

639
00:29:53,572 --> 00:29:55,202
Eun Byul sent the message.

640
00:29:56,502 --> 00:29:58,572
- That means... - Is he getting his hopes up?

641
00:29:59,242 --> 00:30:01,411
Oh, no. What's wrong with his life?

642
00:30:01,412 --> 00:30:02,711
Is he getting his hopes up for nothing?

643
00:30:02,712 --> 00:30:04,941
- It's so sad. - This breaks my heart.

644
00:30:04,942 --> 00:30:06,581
- It hurts! - Gosh.

645
00:30:06,582 --> 00:30:07,951
- Goodness. - This is insane.

646
00:30:07,952 --> 00:30:09,921
You threw away a great girl.

647
00:30:09,922 --> 00:30:11,821
- You really... - He picked Si Woo at first.

648
00:30:11,822 --> 00:30:13,751
- He did. - have bad taste in women.

649
00:30:13,752 --> 00:30:16,361
- Goodness. - Eun Byul is a great girl,

650
00:30:16,362 --> 00:30:18,862
but Jae Seung can't easily change his mind.

651
00:30:19,292 --> 00:30:21,491
Jae Seung picked Si Woo...

652
00:30:21,492 --> 00:30:22,961
for the First Impression Selection.

653
00:30:22,962 --> 00:30:23,962
Do you think...

654
00:30:24,162 --> 00:30:26,032
The ones with "Jae" in their names...

655
00:30:26,072 --> 00:30:28,331
- always stick to their guns. - Really?

656
00:30:28,332 --> 00:30:29,401
You're right.

657
00:30:29,402 --> 00:30:30,402
Who will it be?

658
00:30:30,672 --> 00:30:31,672
Si Woo?

659
00:30:33,212 --> 00:30:36,442
(Who did Jae Seung pick?)

660
00:30:43,322 --> 00:30:46,422
(I'll look forward to your egg fried rice.)

661
00:30:47,092 --> 00:30:48,321
(Jae Seung picked Yu Bin.)

662
00:30:48,322 --> 00:30:49,962
I picked Yu Bin.

663
00:30:51,062 --> 00:30:52,392
- Jae Seung picked Yu Bin? - Jae Seung?

664
00:30:52,792 --> 00:30:54,461
- But you stick to your guns. - Seriously?

665
00:30:54,462 --> 00:30:55,661
- You were wrong. - That's sticking to his guns?

666
00:30:55,662 --> 00:30:57,002
Jae Seung!

667
00:30:57,062 --> 00:30:58,802
He changed his mind before midnight.

668
00:30:59,102 --> 00:31:00,972
- But he sticks to his guns! - Jae Seung!

669
00:31:01,132 --> 00:31:03,142
- What? - He's pretty fickle.

670
00:31:03,542 --> 00:31:04,542
(The romanticist isn't romantic anymore.)

671
00:31:04,543 --> 00:31:05,642
Hey, romanticist!

672
00:31:06,912 --> 00:31:08,611
- What a mean guy. - He's very fickle.

673
00:31:08,612 --> 00:31:10,611
He's been talking to Si Woo all day,

674
00:31:10,612 --> 00:31:12,311
but he picked Yu Bin.

675
00:31:12,312 --> 00:31:14,282
I think he was disappointed after talking to her.

676
00:31:15,582 --> 00:31:17,951
Si Woo's father is also here,

677
00:31:17,952 --> 00:31:19,951
so please watch your words.

678
00:31:19,952 --> 00:31:22,162
- Well, we'll see how it goes. - Sure.

679
00:31:23,022 --> 00:31:25,391
I want to apologize on his behalf.

680
00:31:25,392 --> 00:31:26,632
Gosh.

681
00:31:26,792 --> 00:31:28,902
(Why did you pick Yu Bin?)

682
00:31:28,962 --> 00:31:31,162
She was sitting to my left...

683
00:31:31,802 --> 00:31:34,131
when we were having drinks, and I've been...

684
00:31:34,132 --> 00:31:35,442
talking to her.

685
00:31:35,972 --> 00:31:38,171
I thought it might be nice...

686
00:31:38,172 --> 00:31:41,272
to talk to her in private, so I picked her.

687
00:31:42,742 --> 00:31:49,982
(Lee Jae Seung chose Choi Yu Bin.)

688
00:31:50,622 --> 00:31:53,522
(Who will get the message next?)

689
00:31:58,192 --> 00:32:00,931
(It was nice talking to you while doing the dishes.)

690
00:32:00,932 --> 00:32:03,431
(I hope to get to know you better.)

691
00:32:03,432 --> 00:32:05,161
- Si Woo also got one. - Si Woo got one too.

692
00:32:05,162 --> 00:32:06,371
- Naturally. - Si Woo.

693
00:32:06,372 --> 00:32:07,672
Who sent her the message?

694
00:32:07,702 --> 00:32:08,871
(Who sent the message?)

695
00:32:08,872 --> 00:32:10,242
- I wonder who it is. - Who will it be?

696
00:32:11,072 --> 00:32:14,571
The moment I saw it, I knew...

697
00:32:14,572 --> 00:32:15,582
it was Jae Hyuk.

698
00:32:16,242 --> 00:32:19,612
I was certain about Si Woo in this selection.

699
00:32:20,252 --> 00:32:24,152
I mentioned doing the dishes so that she'd know.

700
00:32:24,982 --> 00:32:27,151
I was hoping...

701
00:32:27,152 --> 00:32:30,292
she would see that I had feelings for her.

702
00:32:31,362 --> 00:32:33,591
I was determined to work for it,

703
00:32:33,592 --> 00:32:35,231
and I couldn't help but be straightforward.

704
00:32:35,232 --> 00:32:36,332
(Jae Hyuk bravely told her his feelings.)

705
00:32:36,702 --> 00:32:39,572
- He just goes forward. - He does.

706
00:32:39,702 --> 00:32:40,831
- That's admirable. - Yes.

707
00:32:40,832 --> 00:32:42,942
Jae Hyuk is truly manly.

708
00:32:43,602 --> 00:32:45,072
Are you saying Jae Seung is girly?

709
00:32:46,442 --> 00:32:48,441
When he's talking to himself...

710
00:32:48,442 --> 00:32:50,141
- But I heard it. - He was talking to himself.

711
00:32:50,142 --> 00:32:52,211
Your son just picked my daughter.

712
00:32:52,212 --> 00:32:53,352
Are you sure you want to do this?

713
00:32:53,882 --> 00:32:55,681
- Did Jae Seung do anything wrong? - He was...

714
00:32:55,682 --> 00:32:58,551
- He was comforting me. - Was that it?

715
00:32:58,552 --> 00:32:59,821
Okay, then.

716
00:32:59,822 --> 00:33:01,822
(He calms down, thinking about his son.)

717
00:33:02,292 --> 00:33:06,532
(Who did Si Woo choose?)

718
00:33:06,832 --> 00:33:11,001
It felt like I wasn't so obvious with my feelings.

719
00:33:11,002 --> 00:33:13,601
So, I tried to express them through the message.

720
00:33:13,602 --> 00:33:15,972
But I'm not sure if he'll recognize me.

721
00:33:16,642 --> 00:33:19,772
(Her First Impression Selection was Hoo.)

722
00:33:20,512 --> 00:33:24,082
(Jae Hyuk continues to express his feelings for her.)

723
00:33:25,042 --> 00:33:28,082
(And Hee Dong gave her flowers.)

724
00:33:28,582 --> 00:33:31,422
(Who did Si Woo pick?)

725
00:33:32,422 --> 00:33:35,591
(You must have been hungry. Enjoy the food!)

726
00:33:35,592 --> 00:33:39,361
I sent my message to Hee Dong in the Attraction Selection.

727
00:33:39,362 --> 00:33:40,431
(She chose Hee Dong.)

728
00:33:40,432 --> 00:33:42,101
- All right. - He got one.

729
00:33:42,102 --> 00:33:43,462
- "You must have been hungry." - That sounds cute.

730
00:33:43,662 --> 00:33:44,762
"Enjoy the food!"

731
00:33:45,332 --> 00:33:47,432
Poor Jae Hyuk. He really sticks to his guns.

732
00:33:47,472 --> 00:33:49,402
Is Jae Hyuk being dumped again?

733
00:33:49,902 --> 00:33:50,902
Oh, dear.

734
00:33:50,903 --> 00:33:53,511
Hee Dong was really enjoying the food...

735
00:33:53,512 --> 00:33:55,641
across the table.

736
00:33:55,642 --> 00:33:58,482
He was eating as if he had starved for a few days.

737
00:34:00,052 --> 00:34:03,922
So, I wrote, "You must have been hungry. Enjoy the food."

738
00:34:04,252 --> 00:34:07,792
Was it, "You must have been hungry. Was it delicious?"

739
00:34:08,192 --> 00:34:10,662
But she wrote it...

740
00:34:11,392 --> 00:34:13,262
kind of cute.

741
00:34:13,362 --> 00:34:16,502
The vibe told me it was Yu Bin.

742
00:34:16,902 --> 00:34:20,001
- Oh, he thinks it's Yu Bin. - He's mistaken.

743
00:34:20,002 --> 00:34:21,901
- Because Yu Bin was... - Right.

744
00:34:21,902 --> 00:34:23,171
He thinks it's from Yu Bin.

745
00:34:23,172 --> 00:34:25,471
- He could... - You're right!

746
00:34:25,472 --> 00:34:27,312
- I can see... - He's really mistaken.

747
00:34:28,212 --> 00:34:33,982
(He thinks Si Woo's message is from Yu Bin.)

748
00:34:34,512 --> 00:34:37,422
(Who will be chosen next for the Attraction Selection?)

749
00:34:43,862 --> 00:34:47,431
(Your steak was better, Hoo.)

750
00:34:47,432 --> 00:34:48,861
- Oh, my son. - He's got one!

751
00:34:48,862 --> 00:34:50,161
- He got a message. - Hoo got a message too.

752
00:34:50,162 --> 00:34:51,261
"Your steak was better!"

753
00:34:51,262 --> 00:34:52,701
Who wrote that?

754
00:34:52,702 --> 00:34:54,571
He's still got it!

755
00:34:54,572 --> 00:34:56,072
- He's still got it. - Who sent it?

756
00:34:56,142 --> 00:34:57,742
But Jae Hyuk also cooked steak.

757
00:34:58,272 --> 00:35:01,541
"Your steak was better, Hoo."

758
00:35:01,542 --> 00:35:02,742
That was the message.

759
00:35:03,482 --> 00:35:05,712
I thought it was Yu Bin.

760
00:35:06,752 --> 00:35:09,952
I was really torn about whom to pick.

761
00:35:10,082 --> 00:35:12,552
I feel close with and thankful...

762
00:35:12,652 --> 00:35:15,022
for Hoo.

763
00:35:15,092 --> 00:35:17,991
And my other favorite is Hee Dong.

764
00:35:17,992 --> 00:35:20,331
We talked a lot...

765
00:35:20,332 --> 00:35:21,761
while playing that board game.

766
00:35:21,762 --> 00:35:25,362
And he has the looks that I'm attracted to.

767
00:35:26,072 --> 00:35:28,632
I'm not sure how I feel.

768
00:35:29,002 --> 00:35:30,102
I thought hard...

769
00:35:31,402 --> 00:35:34,572
and sent it to Hoo.

770
00:35:35,412 --> 00:35:36,412
(Yu Bin chose Hoo.)

771
00:35:36,412 --> 00:35:37,412
Good.

772
00:35:37,712 --> 00:35:40,581
He's been carrying my bags all day...

773
00:35:40,582 --> 00:35:42,181
and cooked delicious food for me.

774
00:35:42,182 --> 00:35:43,852
I feel really close.

775
00:35:44,622 --> 00:35:47,152
We're on the same wavelength, and I feel comfortable around him.

776
00:35:48,322 --> 00:35:50,521
So, I picked Hoo.

777
00:35:50,522 --> 00:35:54,662
(Choi Yu Bin chose Yoon Hoo.)

778
00:35:56,132 --> 00:36:00,372
(Who did Hoo pick, then?)

779
00:36:02,072 --> 00:36:04,372
- I'm the same. Time passed, - Right.

780
00:36:04,772 --> 00:36:05,812
and I felt fine.

781
00:36:06,242 --> 00:36:08,671
(You made my day...)

782
00:36:08,672 --> 00:36:11,112
(with your positivity and cheerful attitude!)

783
00:36:12,412 --> 00:36:16,352
I picked Yu Bin.

784
00:36:16,682 --> 00:36:17,881
Yu Bin got two messages!

785
00:36:17,882 --> 00:36:19,021
(Impressed)

786
00:36:19,022 --> 00:36:21,622
- She's the new star! - Yu Bin!

787
00:36:22,092 --> 00:36:24,421
- She's earned it today. - She's becoming the new star.

788
00:36:24,422 --> 00:36:25,492
(The parents with daughters are disappointed.)

789
00:36:25,792 --> 00:36:27,491
I was able to express...

790
00:36:27,492 --> 00:36:30,131
my feelings more, thanks to Yu Bin.

791
00:36:30,132 --> 00:36:33,501
She was friendly at first,

792
00:36:33,502 --> 00:36:35,032
so I was able to match that...

793
00:36:35,202 --> 00:36:37,572
and expressed a lot of things.

794
00:36:37,602 --> 00:36:39,641
She made my day...

795
00:36:39,642 --> 00:36:43,142
happier.

796
00:36:43,942 --> 00:36:47,252
I certainly want to get to know her more.

797
00:36:48,552 --> 00:36:51,381
They chose each other for the First Impression Selection...

798
00:36:51,382 --> 00:36:52,651
- and the Attraction Selection. - They did.

799
00:36:52,652 --> 00:36:53,821
- That's nice. - Hoo and Yu Bin.

800
00:36:53,822 --> 00:36:55,721
- Let's keep it this way. - Yes.

801
00:36:55,722 --> 00:36:57,122
(The dads are satisfied with the outcome.)

802
00:36:57,422 --> 00:36:58,491
I can talk more.

803
00:36:58,492 --> 00:37:00,362
(Currently, Si Woo has 1 vote,)

804
00:37:00,962 --> 00:37:03,602
(and Yu Bin has 2 votes.)

805
00:37:04,402 --> 00:37:07,572
(Lastly, Hee Dong's choice remains.)

806
00:37:14,872 --> 00:37:16,441
- No way! - No!

807
00:37:16,442 --> 00:37:18,312
"Thanks for helping me loosen up."

808
00:37:18,882 --> 00:37:20,582
Yu Bin got his message!

809
00:37:20,952 --> 00:37:22,751
- She has three messages. - Three.

810
00:37:22,752 --> 00:37:24,152
Goodness.

811
00:37:25,722 --> 00:37:31,392
(Thanks for helping me loosen up.)

812
00:37:32,122 --> 00:37:33,832
I thought it was a mistake.

813
00:37:34,862 --> 00:37:36,461
I thought you were pulling a prank.

814
00:37:36,462 --> 00:37:39,932
I thought, "What? Why do I have three messages?"

815
00:37:40,172 --> 00:37:43,472
I picked Yu Bin for the Attraction Selection.

816
00:37:43,672 --> 00:37:46,711
I was pretty nervous when I first got here.

817
00:37:46,712 --> 00:37:50,742
But she approached me first suggesting we play a board game.

818
00:37:51,912 --> 00:37:56,382
(Do you want to play a board game?)

819
00:37:56,522 --> 00:37:58,722
I felt relaxed from that moment.

820
00:37:59,252 --> 00:38:01,092
So, I wanted to thank her for that.

821
00:38:02,522 --> 00:38:04,862
It doesn't feel real.

822
00:38:05,092 --> 00:38:06,832
On one hand, I'm also worried.

823
00:38:07,192 --> 00:38:09,861
Like, "How should I make up my mind?"

824
00:38:09,862 --> 00:38:13,002
So, I have a lot on my mind.

825
00:38:13,332 --> 00:38:17,102
But I had so much fun, and thank you for today.

826
00:38:17,302 --> 00:38:21,042
I won't be able to forget this Christmas.

827
00:38:23,182 --> 00:38:25,042
- Totally. - She's right.

828
00:38:25,752 --> 00:38:28,151
- That's so nice. - She got a Christmas gift.

829
00:38:28,152 --> 00:38:29,882
It's Yu Bin's landslide victory.

830
00:38:30,722 --> 00:38:31,722
How did things change so fast?

831
00:38:31,723 --> 00:38:32,991
- When I... - These two switched.

832
00:38:32,992 --> 00:38:35,621
sent her to camp at first...

833
00:38:35,622 --> 00:38:37,361
- Camp? This isn't a camp. - It's not.

834
00:38:37,362 --> 00:38:38,491
Do you think this is...

835
00:38:38,492 --> 00:38:40,792
- It's not... - What is this? A summer camp?

836
00:38:40,962 --> 00:38:43,232
Don't call it a camp.

837
00:38:43,332 --> 00:38:44,462
Do you think this is an English camp?

838
00:38:44,932 --> 00:38:47,831
When Yu Bin first told me she'd come here,

839
00:38:47,832 --> 00:38:49,741
- she's honestly not that pretty... - She's beautiful!

840
00:38:49,742 --> 00:38:50,942
or tall.

841
00:38:51,742 --> 00:38:53,171
I told her not to get her feelings hurt...

842
00:38:53,172 --> 00:38:55,711
- and to enjoy the food, at least. - I see.

843
00:38:55,712 --> 00:38:57,641
Now that this is happening,

844
00:38:57,642 --> 00:38:59,711
- I can't... - You're tearing up.

845
00:38:59,712 --> 00:39:00,911
(He gets emotional about the 3 unexpected votes.)

846
00:39:00,912 --> 00:39:04,482
Si Woo got three votes in the First Impression Selection.

847
00:39:04,952 --> 00:39:07,792
This is an honor for my whole family.

848
00:39:09,162 --> 00:39:10,691
I can't believe how it turned out.

849
00:39:10,692 --> 00:39:11,692
(Anxious)

850
00:39:11,762 --> 00:39:14,462
Si Woo's dad is talking significantly less now.

851
00:39:15,092 --> 00:39:16,902
He suddenly seems tired.

852
00:39:17,232 --> 00:39:18,661
He's clearly less excited now.

853
00:39:18,662 --> 00:39:20,431
I mean,

854
00:39:20,432 --> 00:39:22,441
no one's looking at Si Woo right now, so...

855
00:39:22,442 --> 00:39:23,471
- Exactly. - Yes.

856
00:39:23,472 --> 00:39:25,741
He's feeling rushed.

857
00:39:25,742 --> 00:39:26,811
I can tell.

858
00:39:26,812 --> 00:39:29,542
Jae Won is the only one who can't stop smiling.

859
00:39:29,742 --> 00:39:31,982
- This is... - It's amazing.

860
00:39:33,782 --> 00:39:37,452
(And they receive another text message.)

861
00:39:38,152 --> 00:39:39,821
(All feelings have been delivered.)

862
00:39:39,822 --> 00:39:41,751
(The Attraction Selection ends.)

863
00:39:41,752 --> 00:39:42,762
Yes.

864
00:39:44,822 --> 00:39:46,991
(Followed by the First Impression Selection,)

865
00:39:46,992 --> 00:39:49,102
(Eun Byul wasn't chosen by anyone in the Attraction Selection.)

866
00:39:49,262 --> 00:39:52,901
I just feel frustrated.

867
00:39:52,902 --> 00:39:55,802
I should be talking to everyone,

868
00:39:56,372 --> 00:39:59,711
but I don't know why I'm overthinking it.

869
00:39:59,712 --> 00:40:01,412
It's so hard to say something.

870
00:40:01,642 --> 00:40:04,082
This is harder than I imagined.

871
00:40:07,412 --> 00:40:08,952
It's only the first day.

872
00:40:10,122 --> 00:40:12,891
Eun Byul has charms that become apparent with time.

873
00:40:12,892 --> 00:40:15,122
- Of course. - You never know what'll happen.

874
00:40:15,252 --> 00:40:16,521
- That's right. - It's only the first day.

875
00:40:16,522 --> 00:40:18,622
- Her charms will come out. - They'll surely come out.

876
00:40:19,232 --> 00:40:20,431
It'll be the first meeting.

877
00:40:20,432 --> 00:40:22,762
(All feelings have been delivered. The Attraction Selection ends.)

878
00:40:23,062 --> 00:40:26,232
(Jae Hyuk belatedly checks the text message.)

879
00:40:27,002 --> 00:40:28,072
My goodness.

880
00:40:28,402 --> 00:40:29,872
I just wanted to go home.

881
00:40:31,072 --> 00:40:34,142
I received the text message in front of everyone,

882
00:40:34,612 --> 00:40:36,442
so it was hard to school my face.

883
00:40:38,042 --> 00:40:40,652
Gosh, there's no need to be disappointed.

884
00:40:44,652 --> 00:40:46,621
Jae Hyuk, it's nothing.

885
00:40:46,622 --> 00:40:47,821
- It's nothing. - He must be upset.

886
00:40:47,822 --> 00:40:49,721
- As a dad, my heart aches. - My goodness.

887
00:40:49,722 --> 00:40:50,792
- It does, right? - Yes.

888
00:40:52,062 --> 00:40:53,631
I don't know why boys leave Eun Byul alone...

889
00:40:53,632 --> 00:40:55,661
- when she's so beautiful. - Exactly.

890
00:40:55,662 --> 00:40:57,762
I let go of all expectations.

891
00:40:57,862 --> 00:40:59,731
I'm looking into multiple men...

892
00:40:59,732 --> 00:41:01,432
so that I can set up a blind date for my daughter.

893
00:41:03,402 --> 00:41:04,872
You're very upset, right?

894
00:41:04,972 --> 00:41:06,272
Words can't describe this feeling.

895
00:41:07,912 --> 00:41:10,341
- I see. - But my kid doesn't have any flair.

896
00:41:10,342 --> 00:41:11,711
- No? - What you see...

897
00:41:11,712 --> 00:41:13,851
is her authentic self.

898
00:41:13,852 --> 00:41:16,951
In my opinion, she's pretty, nice, and beautiful...

899
00:41:16,952 --> 00:41:19,222
as she is.

900
00:41:19,252 --> 00:41:20,852
But only adults recognize...

901
00:41:20,922 --> 00:41:22,891
- her true worth. - That's right.

902
00:41:22,892 --> 00:41:24,491
- I agree. - Kids can't see it.

903
00:41:24,492 --> 00:41:27,292
- It's frustrating. - There's Jae Seung.

904
00:41:27,592 --> 00:41:28,662
Jae Seung?

905
00:41:29,632 --> 00:41:30,762
For goodness' sake.

906
00:41:31,332 --> 00:41:32,702
What?

907
00:41:32,772 --> 00:41:34,772
Jae Seung will go to Eun Byul.

908
00:41:34,902 --> 00:41:36,672
Right now... All right.

909
00:41:37,002 --> 00:41:38,372
Coach Shin Tae Yong, are you okay?

910
00:41:38,772 --> 00:41:40,771
My heart aches.

911
00:41:40,772 --> 00:41:43,211
My heart aches even more...

912
00:41:43,212 --> 00:41:45,012
- to see my kid's heart ache. - Right.

913
00:41:45,212 --> 00:41:48,852
We entered this show to be happy, but...

914
00:41:49,982 --> 00:41:52,351
- It hasn't ended yet! - But still,

915
00:41:52,352 --> 00:41:53,721
that's the current reality.

916
00:41:53,722 --> 00:41:55,022
- Only some people are happy. - Yes.

917
00:41:56,022 --> 00:41:58,362
He's talking big since his kid received three votes.

918
00:41:58,562 --> 00:42:00,132
- He's acting spoiled. - Yes.

919
00:42:00,232 --> 00:42:03,061
With time, Jae Hyuk's charms will come out.

920
00:42:03,062 --> 00:42:05,531
- Then things will change. - Things will change indeed.

921
00:42:05,532 --> 00:42:06,832
- I believe in him. - Right.

922
00:42:07,832 --> 00:42:09,031
(First Attraction Selection)

923
00:42:09,032 --> 00:42:10,641
(Shin Jae Hyuk chose Park Si Woo.)

924
00:42:10,642 --> 00:42:12,171
(Yoon Hoo, Lee Jae Seung, and You Hee Dong chose Choi Yu Bin.)

925
00:42:12,172 --> 00:42:13,771
(1 vote, 3 votes, 0 votes)

926
00:42:13,772 --> 00:42:14,841
(Park Si Woo chose You Hee Dong. Choi Yu Bin chose Yoon Hoo.)

927
00:42:14,842 --> 00:42:17,311
(Cho Eun Byul chose Lee Jae Seung.)

928
00:42:17,312 --> 00:42:19,782
(1 vote, 1 vote, 0 votes, 1 vote)

929
00:42:20,412 --> 00:42:24,152
(The Attraction Selection with many twists ends.)

930
00:42:24,582 --> 00:42:27,322
(Kids go back to their rooms.)

931
00:42:27,992 --> 00:42:30,662
(Si Woo and Eun Byul's room)

932
00:42:36,732 --> 00:42:39,002
- You're deep in thought. - Yes.

933
00:42:39,702 --> 00:42:41,272
- Is it obvious? - Yes.

934
00:42:43,602 --> 00:42:44,841
I... I don't know.

935
00:42:44,842 --> 00:42:47,641
I don't know how the other person feels.

936
00:42:47,642 --> 00:42:48,672
I see.

937
00:42:50,382 --> 00:42:51,882
She's unsure.

938
00:42:52,282 --> 00:42:55,352
- Hee Dong gave her flowers, - That's right.

939
00:42:55,512 --> 00:42:57,251
but he didn't choose her for the Attraction Selection.

940
00:42:57,252 --> 00:42:59,121
- She's like, "What's this?" - "What's this?"

941
00:42:59,122 --> 00:43:01,122
- She's unsure. - She doesn't understand him.

942
00:43:01,552 --> 00:43:02,922
Hee Dong is a bit...

943
00:43:03,162 --> 00:43:06,631
Perhaps I'm overthinking it,

944
00:43:06,632 --> 00:43:08,831
but I don't know what's going on in his mind.

945
00:43:08,832 --> 00:43:10,902
It makes me curious about him.

946
00:43:11,062 --> 00:43:13,172
I can't predict anything about him.

947
00:43:14,632 --> 00:43:16,341
(Whom do you think Hee Dong chose?)

948
00:43:16,342 --> 00:43:17,672
I think...

949
00:43:18,102 --> 00:43:20,912
he sent a text message to Yu Bin.

950
00:43:21,172 --> 00:43:25,212
The two of them seemed to get along very well.

951
00:43:25,312 --> 00:43:27,312
They talked a lot too.

952
00:43:27,752 --> 00:43:29,181
It's understandable.

953
00:43:29,182 --> 00:43:31,481
He just arrived here,

954
00:43:31,482 --> 00:43:33,521
so he'd want to get to know people.

955
00:43:33,522 --> 00:43:36,292
I think it's understandable.

956
00:43:37,592 --> 00:43:39,231
(Si Woo predicts that Hee Dong chose Yu Bin.)

957
00:43:39,232 --> 00:43:41,091
- She has a hunch. - Did she observe them?

958
00:43:41,092 --> 00:43:43,002
She's sharp.

959
00:43:44,132 --> 00:43:46,132
(In the room of Si Woo who became thoughtful)

960
00:43:47,572 --> 00:43:50,271
- What are you guys up to? - Yu Bin visited.

961
00:43:50,272 --> 00:43:52,372
- Hey, that room is... - She couldn't read the room.

962
00:43:52,472 --> 00:43:53,972
- She could've waited. - Come on in.

963
00:43:54,672 --> 00:43:57,382
How is everything doing?

964
00:43:58,142 --> 00:44:00,781
Compared to our very first meeting,

965
00:44:00,782 --> 00:44:02,981
- you seem more relaxed. - Yes, I've adjusted.

966
00:44:02,982 --> 00:44:04,322
- I see. - Thank goodness.

967
00:44:04,582 --> 00:44:06,392
Can I...

968
00:44:06,592 --> 00:44:08,592
- Can I ask you a question? - Okay.

969
00:44:08,892 --> 00:44:10,722
- A question? - A question?

970
00:44:12,862 --> 00:44:16,032
Is there someone you're interested in?

971
00:44:16,632 --> 00:44:17,931
She asked that right away.

972
00:44:17,932 --> 00:44:19,272
Already?

973
00:44:19,672 --> 00:44:20,672
Is there?

974
00:44:21,932 --> 00:44:23,872
- I'm not sure yet. - Really?

975
00:44:24,272 --> 00:44:27,411
There isn't anyone I absolutely like.

976
00:44:27,412 --> 00:44:30,111
But there are people I want to know better.

977
00:44:30,112 --> 00:44:33,611
Things will feel very different when we have a 1-on-1 conversation.

978
00:44:33,612 --> 00:44:36,522
But we haven't had a chance to do that.

979
00:44:37,082 --> 00:44:39,151
I had ice cream with Yoon Hoo...

980
00:44:39,152 --> 00:44:40,821
- earlier. - I see.

981
00:44:40,822 --> 00:44:43,091
We talked in a relaxed manner...

982
00:44:43,092 --> 00:44:45,722
like friends, so it was enjoyable.

983
00:44:45,922 --> 00:44:47,762
I felt like I had already gained a friend.

984
00:44:48,632 --> 00:44:51,101
The person you want to get to know...

985
00:44:51,102 --> 00:44:54,632
and the person you want to befriend are different.

986
00:44:54,902 --> 00:44:58,202
Did you send a text message to both?

987
00:44:58,572 --> 00:44:59,642
To both?

988
00:44:59,772 --> 00:45:01,941
The one you want to befriend...

989
00:45:01,942 --> 00:45:03,642
and the one you want to get to know.

990
00:45:05,782 --> 00:45:07,581
No, I...

991
00:45:07,582 --> 00:45:10,721
only sent it to someone I wanted to befriend...

992
00:45:10,722 --> 00:45:12,051
after some deliberation.

993
00:45:12,052 --> 00:45:15,522
(Yu Bin chose someone she was comfortable around.)

994
00:45:15,692 --> 00:45:17,591
(If you exclude Yoon Hoo, who is on your mind the most?)

995
00:45:17,592 --> 00:45:18,922
For me, it's Hee Dong.

996
00:45:19,122 --> 00:45:21,291
It's just a guess, but I feel like...

997
00:45:21,292 --> 00:45:25,402
one of those text messages is from him.

998
00:45:25,762 --> 00:45:27,572
So I want to talk to Hee Dong.

999
00:45:30,072 --> 00:45:32,971
Yu Bin felt like she had already gained a friend.

1000
00:45:32,972 --> 00:45:34,012
Yes.

1001
00:45:34,112 --> 00:45:36,642
She wants Hoo as a friend...

1002
00:45:36,882 --> 00:45:38,441
and Hee Dong as a boyfriend.

1003
00:45:38,442 --> 00:45:39,711
(Does she want Hee Dong as a boyfriend?)

1004
00:45:39,712 --> 00:45:40,881
Isn't that it?

1005
00:45:40,882 --> 00:45:42,381
A friend versus...

1006
00:45:42,382 --> 00:45:44,122
- a boyfriend. - Yes.

1007
00:45:47,522 --> 00:45:48,992
What are you drinking?

1008
00:45:49,492 --> 00:45:50,592
I can't sleep.

1009
00:45:51,792 --> 00:45:53,162
Do you usually have trouble sleeping?

1010
00:45:54,232 --> 00:45:55,932
- A little bit. - A little bit?

1011
00:45:58,362 --> 00:45:59,971
You can sit at the front.

1012
00:45:59,972 --> 00:46:01,302
The furnace is still warm.

1013
00:46:02,232 --> 00:46:04,371
- He guided her to six next to him. - Just like that?

1014
00:46:04,372 --> 00:46:06,511
He told her to take the warm seat...

1015
00:46:06,512 --> 00:46:09,012
- next to his. - Gosh, that's...

1016
00:46:09,582 --> 00:46:12,311
- He's sweet. - My goodness.

1017
00:46:12,312 --> 00:46:13,912
He's better than his dad.

1018
00:46:14,352 --> 00:46:15,382
It's warm.

1019
00:46:16,922 --> 00:46:19,122
I could fall asleep in front of the furnace.

1020
00:46:21,192 --> 00:46:22,192
That sounds nice.

1021
00:46:22,962 --> 00:46:25,192
Please take my drowsiness.

1022
00:46:26,162 --> 00:46:28,492
(They joke around with ease.)

1023
00:46:28,532 --> 00:46:30,602
Do you know...

1024
00:46:31,232 --> 00:46:32,632
how to turn off the lights in the room?

1025
00:46:32,772 --> 00:46:33,772
What?

1026
00:46:34,032 --> 00:46:36,771
"Do you know how do turn off the lights?"

1027
00:46:36,772 --> 00:46:39,141
- Why did he come out? - Can't Jae Seung do it himself?

1028
00:46:39,142 --> 00:46:40,542
Can't Jae Seung turn off the lights?

1029
00:46:41,412 --> 00:46:42,781
Please turn off the lights.

1030
00:46:42,782 --> 00:46:44,542
Isn't this the switch? Why doesn't it work?

1031
00:46:45,782 --> 00:46:48,182
You can go back. We'll look for it.

1032
00:46:48,712 --> 00:46:50,852
- Good night. - Good night.

1033
00:46:51,352 --> 00:46:52,352
What are you doing?

1034
00:46:53,292 --> 00:46:54,622
Let's try this.

1035
00:46:55,892 --> 00:46:56,892
What is it?

1036
00:46:56,893 --> 00:46:58,691
You open the book to a page for a fortune reading.

1037
00:46:58,692 --> 00:47:01,232
Is it real? I thought it was a fake book.

1038
00:47:01,562 --> 00:47:03,002
Since it's past midnight,

1039
00:47:03,532 --> 00:47:06,902
we should do a fortune reading for today.

1040
00:47:07,602 --> 00:47:08,632
Go first.

1041
00:47:08,802 --> 00:47:11,602
When I checked earlier, it said that I had crossed the line.

1042
00:47:12,242 --> 00:47:13,472
- Did your fortune reading say that? - Yes.

1043
00:47:13,772 --> 00:47:17,212
The written words will give us our fortune for tomorrow.

1044
00:47:18,442 --> 00:47:19,682
- Did your fortune reading say that? - Yes.

1045
00:47:19,782 --> 00:47:22,082
Which one of you has nice handwriting?

1046
00:47:22,712 --> 00:47:24,081
(He shows up when the atmosphere turns romantic.)

1047
00:47:24,082 --> 00:47:25,782
- Do you? - No.

1048
00:47:26,452 --> 00:47:28,292
I don't have nice handwriting either.

1049
00:47:30,762 --> 00:47:32,962
(Sighing)

1050
00:47:33,032 --> 00:47:35,231
- Jae Seung, read the room! - For goodness' sake.

1051
00:47:35,232 --> 00:47:37,102
Why wouldn't the light go off?

1052
00:47:37,502 --> 00:47:40,702
(Hoo's dad finds it funny.)

1053
00:47:46,772 --> 00:47:48,342
Are you reading?

1054
00:47:48,712 --> 00:47:51,642
It gives you today's fortune.

1055
00:47:52,182 --> 00:47:54,252
I thought you were smart.

1056
00:47:54,712 --> 00:47:56,151
I can't believe it.

1057
00:47:56,152 --> 00:47:58,622
- I think he came to tease Hoo. - Good night.

1058
00:47:59,592 --> 00:48:00,991
You should sleep with the light turned on.

1059
00:48:00,992 --> 00:48:02,292
(Thus, everyone goes back to the room.)

1060
00:48:03,362 --> 00:48:04,962
- Get some rest. - Bye.

1061
00:48:06,732 --> 00:48:10,702
(Hoo goes back to his room feeling disappointed.)

1062
00:48:19,172 --> 00:48:21,211
(Suddenly, he goes back out.)

1063
00:48:21,212 --> 00:48:22,372
That was sudden.

1064
00:48:32,382 --> 00:48:34,692
- Gosh. - Gosh, you're too hurried.

1065
00:48:34,922 --> 00:48:36,222
Hoo, slow down.

1066
00:48:36,562 --> 00:48:38,792
(He passes the Photo Room...)

1067
00:48:39,732 --> 00:48:41,762
(and arrives at the Letter Room.)

1068
00:48:48,202 --> 00:48:50,942
Despite everything, I wanted to express my feelings...

1069
00:48:51,442 --> 00:48:53,212
as a tough guy.

1070
00:48:55,172 --> 00:48:56,981
- He wants to express his feelings. - That's right.

1071
00:48:56,982 --> 00:48:58,382
I guess he'll write a letter.

1072
00:48:58,612 --> 00:49:01,452
Hoo springs into action.

1073
00:49:05,352 --> 00:49:06,592
What should I do?

1074
00:49:08,752 --> 00:49:10,162
(Hesitant)

1075
00:49:12,862 --> 00:49:17,102
(After hesitation, he writes the first word.)

1076
00:49:18,802 --> 00:49:19,972
(Thinking)

1077
00:49:22,872 --> 00:49:23,902
(Writing)

1078
00:49:23,972 --> 00:49:27,041
Still, telling someone outright...

1079
00:49:27,042 --> 00:49:30,481
that I'm interested in her...

1080
00:49:30,482 --> 00:49:33,382
is my way.

1081
00:49:36,752 --> 00:49:40,292
(The writing paper is in tatters.)

1082
00:49:42,252 --> 00:49:44,362
(He takes out a new one.)

1083
00:49:50,032 --> 00:49:51,702
I just kept it simple.

1084
00:49:52,262 --> 00:49:53,671
Since we had just met,

1085
00:49:53,672 --> 00:49:56,342
a long letter would've been too much.

1086
00:50:12,652 --> 00:50:16,362
(Will the letter reach the recipient safely?)

1087
00:50:16,762 --> 00:50:18,492
(Meanwhile, Jae Hyuk's room)

1088
00:50:20,762 --> 00:50:22,862
(There's a letter on his bed.)

1089
00:50:23,402 --> 00:50:24,702
What? Did he receive a letter?

1090
00:50:24,862 --> 00:50:26,871
- What? - He isn't in the Letter Room.

1091
00:50:26,872 --> 00:50:28,131
(Someone left Jae Hyuk a letter.)

1092
00:50:28,132 --> 00:50:29,302
Why is there a letter?

1093
00:50:34,772 --> 00:50:35,811
(He finally smiles.)

1094
00:50:35,812 --> 00:50:37,381
- Jae Hyuk smiled. - He smiled.

1095
00:50:37,382 --> 00:50:38,912
- What? - It must be from a resident.

1096
00:50:39,142 --> 00:50:40,681
- Who sent it? - Did someone send a letter...

1097
00:50:40,682 --> 00:50:43,222
- before Yoon Hoo did? - That must be it.

1098
00:50:43,282 --> 00:50:44,721
It's express delivery.

1099
00:50:44,722 --> 00:50:46,051
- It's... - What is it?

1100
00:50:46,052 --> 00:50:47,252
(What's the letter he got via express delivery?)

1101
00:50:48,752 --> 00:50:52,122
"Go to bed first, Jae Hyuk!"

1102
00:50:52,622 --> 00:50:55,492
(It was written by his polite roommate.)

1103
00:50:56,132 --> 00:50:58,002
(Flustered)

1104
00:50:58,832 --> 00:51:01,972
(No one guessed the identity of the sender.)

1105
00:51:03,042 --> 00:51:04,902
- Gosh. - Is he a comedian?

1106
00:51:04,942 --> 00:51:06,302
Gosh, Jae Hyuk.

1107
00:51:06,512 --> 00:51:08,011
My son is so polite.

1108
00:51:08,012 --> 00:51:09,682
Jae Hyuk got disappointed again.

1109
00:51:10,682 --> 00:51:12,012
Gosh, my Jae Hyuk.

1110
00:51:12,482 --> 00:51:14,182
I had hopes when he smiled.

1111
00:51:14,312 --> 00:51:19,382
(The unforgettable Christmas passes.)

1112
00:51:25,992 --> 00:51:29,532
(The daughters wake up early.)

1113
00:51:35,632 --> 00:51:38,702
(Yu Bin finished getting ready and heads outside.)

1114
00:51:45,612 --> 00:51:47,351
(She goes up the stairs...)

1115
00:51:47,352 --> 00:51:50,222
(and arrives at the Letter Room.)

1116
00:51:56,492 --> 00:51:59,792
(She checks her mailbox for letters.)

1117
00:52:04,932 --> 00:52:06,902
(Smiling)

1118
00:52:08,632 --> 00:52:10,641
(Yu Bin's smile makes the dads happy.)

1119
00:52:10,642 --> 00:52:11,642
She likes it.

1120
00:52:15,012 --> 00:52:17,611
(Last night,)

1121
00:52:17,612 --> 00:52:20,682
(Yoon Hoo poured out his heart in the letter.)

1122
00:52:22,382 --> 00:52:28,252
(From the moment we met today, I thought you were a beauty.)

1123
00:52:29,322 --> 00:52:33,361
(Your cheerful and bubbly personality...)

1124
00:52:33,362 --> 00:52:38,202
(put me in a good mood today.)

1125
00:52:38,732 --> 00:52:45,501
(I want to get to know you better over a meal!)

1126
00:52:45,502 --> 00:52:46,972
"Over a meal."

1127
00:52:47,212 --> 00:52:49,042
Why does he sound so homely?

1128
00:52:50,312 --> 00:52:53,282
I like how innocent Hoo is.

1129
00:52:54,882 --> 00:52:57,422
The way he calls her a beauty puts a smile on my face.

1130
00:53:00,422 --> 00:53:05,522
(Her steps become light after reading the letter.)

1131
00:53:07,392 --> 00:53:08,862
(She reads it...)

1132
00:53:09,692 --> 00:53:11,632
(and reads it again.)

1133
00:53:13,402 --> 00:53:17,372
(She puts the letter at a place where she can see it.)

1134
00:53:19,742 --> 00:53:20,971
(Your cheerful and bubbly personality...)

1135
00:53:20,972 --> 00:53:22,211
(put me in a good mood today.)

1136
00:53:22,212 --> 00:53:24,682
(I want to get to know you better over a meal!)

1137
00:53:25,082 --> 00:53:27,882
Hoo wrote the letter at the perfect timing...

1138
00:53:28,352 --> 00:53:30,752
when Yu Bin was about to get swayed.

1139
00:53:30,882 --> 00:53:32,022
Nice timing.

1140
00:53:32,652 --> 00:53:33,922
What do you think of the letter?

1141
00:53:34,552 --> 00:53:37,092
It's nearly perfect.

1142
00:53:37,262 --> 00:53:38,262
- Perfect. - Yes.

1143
00:53:38,263 --> 00:53:39,421
- Seriously. - "Let's have a meal together."

1144
00:53:39,422 --> 00:53:41,991
My future son-in-law wrote a nice letter...

1145
00:53:41,992 --> 00:53:44,432
- to my daughter. - Your future son-in-law?

1146
00:53:45,302 --> 00:53:46,631
Isn't it too soon for that?

1147
00:53:46,632 --> 00:53:49,232
I could feel his innocence.

1148
00:53:49,302 --> 00:53:52,541
I think Hoo made a decisive move.

1149
00:53:52,542 --> 00:53:54,411
- He acted before the others. - Yes.

1150
00:53:54,412 --> 00:53:57,111
That's right. Dads with sons keep going,

1151
00:53:57,112 --> 00:53:58,411
"There'll be a hook."

1152
00:53:58,412 --> 00:54:00,681
- "He'll do something big later." - That's right.

1153
00:54:00,682 --> 00:54:02,782
But little strokes fell great oaks.

1154
00:54:03,322 --> 00:54:04,322
That's right.

1155
00:54:04,323 --> 00:54:05,451
Small things add up.

1156
00:54:05,452 --> 00:54:06,651
- Small things add up. - Yes.

1157
00:54:06,652 --> 00:54:08,691
Is that directed at Jae Hyuk and Jae Seung?

1158
00:54:08,692 --> 00:54:10,492
Yes. Hee Dong should take note too.

1159
00:54:11,292 --> 00:54:12,791
Hoo moved...

1160
00:54:12,792 --> 00:54:14,731
- a bit more quickly. - He's more forward.

1161
00:54:14,732 --> 00:54:15,991
Love is all about the speed.

1162
00:54:15,992 --> 00:54:18,162
That's right. The timing matters.

1163
00:54:19,702 --> 00:54:23,972
(Hoo and Jae Hyuk's room)

1164
00:54:24,742 --> 00:54:29,242
(The man who wrote the letter, Hoo is still asleep.)

1165
00:54:29,842 --> 00:54:31,911
(Jae Seung and Hee Dong's room)

1166
00:54:31,912 --> 00:54:35,582
(Tossing)

1167
00:54:39,582 --> 00:54:43,922
(Jae Seung is the first to wake up among men.)

1168
00:54:52,062 --> 00:54:54,272
(Halting)

1169
00:54:58,142 --> 00:54:59,802
- What? He got something. - He got something.

1170
00:55:01,042 --> 00:55:04,611
(Gift boxes are outside the door.)

1171
00:55:04,612 --> 00:55:06,981
(Lee Jae Seung, for the recipient only)

1172
00:55:06,982 --> 00:55:08,351
It's a gift box.

1173
00:55:08,352 --> 00:55:09,982
(What's inside the gift box?)

1174
00:55:13,946 --> 00:55:15,476
- What? He got something. - He got something.

1175
00:55:16,816 --> 00:55:20,345
(Gift boxes are outside the door.)

1176
00:55:20,346 --> 00:55:22,715
(Lee Jae Seung, for the recipient only)

1177
00:55:22,716 --> 00:55:24,085
It's a gift box.

1178
00:55:24,086 --> 00:55:25,916
(What's inside the special gift box?)

1179
00:55:26,386 --> 00:55:29,186
When I woke up and went out, I saw a present.

1180
00:55:29,456 --> 00:55:31,096
I wondered if it was a Christmas present.

1181
00:55:31,456 --> 00:55:33,866
I brought it inside the room feeling happy.

1182
00:55:37,096 --> 00:55:42,735
(Jae Seung opens the box.)

1183
00:55:42,736 --> 00:55:47,345
(First-come First-served Date)

1184
00:55:47,346 --> 00:55:51,746
(It's Dad's winning present for a date.)

1185
00:55:52,276 --> 00:55:54,586
Dad's winning present for a date.

1186
00:55:55,346 --> 00:55:57,085
"Deliver the present to the woman of your choice..."

1187
00:55:57,086 --> 00:55:58,785
"and ask her out on a date."

1188
00:55:58,786 --> 00:55:59,916
(They must deliver the present and ask women out on a date.)

1189
00:56:00,056 --> 00:56:02,085
"The dates will take place on a first-come, first-served basis."

1190
00:56:02,086 --> 00:56:04,926
"If your desired date has already matched with another,"

1191
00:56:05,426 --> 00:56:07,625
"you must ask out someone else."

1192
00:56:07,626 --> 00:56:09,795
- Yes. - They just need to act fast.

1193
00:56:09,796 --> 00:56:11,335
(Dads' presents for the First-come First-served Date)

1194
00:56:11,336 --> 00:56:12,736
But there are 4 men and 3 women.

1195
00:56:12,896 --> 00:56:13,905
- Yes. - Yes.

1196
00:56:13,906 --> 00:56:16,106
One man will be left at home.

1197
00:56:16,366 --> 00:56:18,435
- The sons shouldn't be sleeping. - I know.

1198
00:56:18,436 --> 00:56:19,605
- They should wake up. - They should call dibs.

1199
00:56:19,606 --> 00:56:21,806
- That's right. - Jae Seung should run.

1200
00:56:24,116 --> 00:56:26,076
The instructions told me to ask someone out on a date.

1201
00:56:26,216 --> 00:56:28,015
It was on a first-come, first-served basis.

1202
00:56:28,016 --> 00:56:30,616
- That's right. - I was a bit taken aback.

1203
00:56:31,516 --> 00:56:34,356
Inside the box was a present my dad had prepared...

1204
00:56:34,726 --> 00:56:37,126
so that I could hand it over as I asked someone out on a date.

1205
00:56:38,696 --> 00:56:40,925
Which present did his dad prepare?

1206
00:56:40,926 --> 00:56:41,926
I know.

1207
00:56:42,396 --> 00:56:45,466
(I hope it's something my daughter likes.)

1208
00:56:46,136 --> 00:56:47,366
It was a book of poems.

1209
00:56:48,636 --> 00:56:49,736
- A book of poems. - A book of poems?

1210
00:56:50,236 --> 00:56:51,376
- A book of poems. - A book of poems?

1211
00:56:51,606 --> 00:56:53,506
- A book of poems? - A book of poems?

1212
00:56:54,306 --> 00:56:55,605
When I was young,

1213
00:56:55,606 --> 00:56:58,146
men gave a book of poems to women.

1214
00:56:58,716 --> 00:57:00,085
They read poems to women.

1215
00:57:00,086 --> 00:57:02,216
I guess your son was influenced.

1216
00:57:02,646 --> 00:57:04,215
There's a poem by Na Tae Ju,

1217
00:57:04,216 --> 00:57:05,655
- right? - Right.

1218
00:57:05,656 --> 00:57:07,255
"One becomes pretty with frequent meetings."

1219
00:57:07,256 --> 00:57:08,625
"One becomes lovely with a long relationship."

1220
00:57:08,626 --> 00:57:10,596
"You did." When I read such poems to women,

1221
00:57:10,756 --> 00:57:13,056
they became touched.

1222
00:57:14,766 --> 00:57:17,266
But parents with daughters are going,

1223
00:57:17,536 --> 00:57:19,365
- "Will a book of poems work?" - A book of poems?

1224
00:57:19,366 --> 00:57:20,465
They look unimpressed.

1225
00:57:20,466 --> 00:57:21,466
A book of poems.

1226
00:57:21,467 --> 00:57:23,065
- Kids these days won't get it. - No, they won't.

1227
00:57:23,066 --> 00:57:26,806
And while Jae Seung has a poker face,

1228
00:57:27,046 --> 00:57:28,475
he's a bit sentimental.

1229
00:57:28,476 --> 00:57:31,045
His sentimentality will come out when he reads poems.

1230
00:57:31,046 --> 00:57:32,675
He should find himself a girl...

1231
00:57:32,676 --> 00:57:34,685
- who can accept that. - That's right.

1232
00:57:34,686 --> 00:57:36,485
If a girl can't accept that, she won't be a good match.

1233
00:57:36,486 --> 00:57:38,185
I really hope it works out.

1234
00:57:38,186 --> 00:57:39,286
(He wraps it up hurriedly.)

1235
00:57:39,716 --> 00:57:41,226
I'm nervous. What should I do?

1236
00:57:41,486 --> 00:57:43,596
Who will like a book of poems?

1237
00:57:43,756 --> 00:57:45,596
A book of poems might lead to marriage.

1238
00:57:45,856 --> 00:57:48,196
(Shaking his head)

1239
00:57:48,296 --> 00:57:50,996
(Si Woo and Eun Byul's room)

1240
00:57:52,736 --> 00:57:56,706
(Women receive a text message.)

1241
00:58:02,306 --> 00:58:03,915
"Today, there'll be the first date..."

1242
00:58:03,916 --> 00:58:05,376
"that reflects men's preferences."

1243
00:58:05,676 --> 00:58:07,385
"Men will ask women out..."

1244
00:58:07,386 --> 00:58:08,916
"on a first-come, first-served basis."

1245
00:58:09,016 --> 00:58:11,555
"Women can't say no to a date."

1246
00:58:11,556 --> 00:58:12,616
They can't say no.

1247
00:58:14,286 --> 00:58:17,756
When I received a text message about the First-come First-served Date,

1248
00:58:18,096 --> 00:58:21,526
I hoped to get asked out first.

1249
00:58:23,396 --> 00:58:26,166
Men will ask women out on a date.

1250
00:58:26,766 --> 00:58:28,836
It gave me many thoughts...

1251
00:58:29,166 --> 00:58:32,206
and worries. Yes. That's my current state.

1252
00:58:32,976 --> 00:58:34,476
The day before,

1253
00:58:35,206 --> 00:58:39,046
I didn't get any votes for the Attraction Selection.

1254
00:58:39,476 --> 00:58:43,986
So I thought, "I won't go out on a date today."

1255
00:58:44,686 --> 00:58:46,686
Eun Byul is worried that no one will ask her out.

1256
00:58:47,086 --> 00:58:48,725
Eun Byul will get asked out.

1257
00:58:48,726 --> 00:58:50,756
- One man will stay home. - That's right.

1258
00:58:51,596 --> 00:58:54,766
(Dads with sons become nervous.)

1259
00:58:56,126 --> 00:58:58,535
(The sons are still asleep,)

1260
00:58:58,536 --> 00:59:02,036
(unaware of the First-come First-served Date.)

1261
00:59:02,566 --> 00:59:04,305
He even wrote a letter before he went to sleep.

1262
00:59:04,306 --> 00:59:06,506
It's first-come first-served basis, so he needs to hurry.

1263
00:59:07,506 --> 00:59:09,806
Is Jae Seung not going until he wakes up?

1264
00:59:10,416 --> 00:59:11,446
He should hurry.

1265
00:59:18,786 --> 00:59:22,455
(Jae Seung is the first to leave the room.)

1266
00:59:22,456 --> 00:59:24,295
If he's leaving now,

1267
00:59:24,296 --> 00:59:26,456
he could ask anyone out.

1268
00:59:27,796 --> 00:59:29,396
- That's Yu Bin's room. - Yu Bin.

1269
00:59:30,766 --> 00:59:31,936
- What? - What?

1270
00:59:31,996 --> 00:59:33,066
He's not going to Yu Bin's room.

1271
00:59:36,166 --> 00:59:38,636
(He heads to the men's room, not women's.)

1272
00:59:39,106 --> 00:59:40,376
How was your sleep?

1273
00:59:40,976 --> 00:59:43,345
Did you wake up to the sound of the door opening? I'm sorry.

1274
00:59:43,346 --> 00:59:44,615
I'm awake.

1275
00:59:44,616 --> 00:59:45,946
I was so bored.

1276
00:59:47,616 --> 00:59:49,216
Hey, now's not the time to be doing that.

1277
00:59:51,116 --> 00:59:53,386
- Hey. - He's bored?

1278
00:59:53,516 --> 00:59:55,125
You have a present in front.

1279
00:59:55,126 --> 00:59:56,326
Check it out.

1280
00:59:57,526 --> 00:59:58,656
Did something arrive?

1281
00:59:58,996 --> 01:00:00,366
Yes, a present.

1282
01:00:01,566 --> 01:00:03,125
- A present? - Yes.

1283
01:00:03,126 --> 01:00:04,765
Yours is in front of the door.

1284
01:00:04,766 --> 01:00:05,896
(Jae Seung spreads the news like a pigeon.)

1285
01:00:06,596 --> 01:00:09,405
It's first-come first-served, but he didn't leave first.

1286
01:00:09,406 --> 01:00:11,275
He could've just left first.

1287
01:00:11,276 --> 01:00:13,705
He's waking up his competitors.

1288
01:00:13,706 --> 01:00:15,246
How can he do that?

1289
01:00:16,246 --> 01:00:19,245
(Why did you tell everyone?)

1290
01:00:19,246 --> 01:00:21,016
Rather than knowing it...

1291
01:00:21,716 --> 01:00:23,115
and going to them myself,

1292
01:00:23,116 --> 01:00:26,555
I thought it'd be better if everyone knew.

1293
01:00:26,556 --> 01:00:27,556
(He prefers fair play.)

1294
01:00:27,826 --> 01:00:29,755
Jae Seung, what are you doing?

1295
01:00:29,756 --> 01:00:31,226
My goodness.

1296
01:00:37,736 --> 01:00:42,306
(Jae Hyuk takes the gift box in front of his room.)

1297
01:00:43,066 --> 01:00:47,476
(What date present did Tae Yong get?)

1298
01:00:47,876 --> 01:00:49,475
It was perfume.

1299
01:00:49,476 --> 01:00:51,645
(Perfume)

1300
01:00:51,646 --> 01:00:53,315
- Perfume. - Perfume.

1301
01:00:53,316 --> 01:00:55,786
Tae Yong gave perfume to his son.

1302
01:00:56,146 --> 01:00:57,385
- This is a nice gift. - I see.

1303
01:00:57,386 --> 01:00:59,015
Since Jae Hyuk plays sports,

1304
01:00:59,016 --> 01:01:00,755
he smells strongly of sweat.

1305
01:01:00,756 --> 01:01:03,426
I want him to smell refreshing...

1306
01:01:03,586 --> 01:01:05,395
when going on a date with a girl.

1307
01:01:05,396 --> 01:01:07,596
Isn't that supposed to be a gift, not for himself?

1308
01:01:08,966 --> 01:01:10,096
He can spray it on his date.

1309
01:01:10,436 --> 01:01:11,466
He can spray it on his date.

1310
01:01:12,066 --> 01:01:13,195
Everyone has different preferences...

1311
01:01:13,196 --> 01:01:14,935
- in perfume. - Is that so?

1312
01:01:14,936 --> 01:01:17,535
- Depending on the person... - His date will like it.

1313
01:01:17,536 --> 01:01:18,936
- Watch until the end. - Okay.

1314
01:01:19,906 --> 01:01:21,376
I think it's better than a poetry book.

1315
01:01:22,146 --> 01:01:24,946
- Why? - He must've bought a good one.

1316
01:01:25,716 --> 01:01:28,016
My dad likes perfume,

1317
01:01:28,216 --> 01:01:29,986
and so do I.

1318
01:01:30,686 --> 01:01:33,926
I think that's why he chose perfume.

1319
01:01:34,626 --> 01:01:36,625
I hope the person I'm asking out...

1320
01:01:36,626 --> 01:01:38,656
likes it.

1321
01:01:41,366 --> 01:01:42,626
What is he doing?

1322
01:01:43,126 --> 01:01:44,435
He finally got up.

1323
01:01:44,436 --> 01:01:46,396
(Yoon Hoo goes to check the gift box, still half-asleep.)

1324
01:01:52,376 --> 01:01:54,246
It's behind you, Hoo.

1325
01:01:54,606 --> 01:01:56,776
He's still not fully awake. What's wrong with him?

1326
01:01:57,416 --> 01:01:59,416
(Staggering)

1327
01:02:04,286 --> 01:02:05,316
Where is he going?

1328
01:02:07,226 --> 01:02:08,256
It's cold.

1329
01:02:27,406 --> 01:02:28,445
(He spots it.)

1330
01:02:28,446 --> 01:02:29,676
- He found it. - He saw it.

1331
01:02:31,716 --> 01:02:32,776
He's so funny.

1332
01:02:33,516 --> 01:02:35,016
- He's just like when he was young. - He really is.

1333
01:02:36,116 --> 01:02:37,485
(What present did Min Soo get?)

1334
01:02:37,486 --> 01:02:39,356
My father got...

1335
01:02:39,956 --> 01:02:43,686
a pair of gloves and earmuffs.

1336
01:02:44,726 --> 01:02:46,155
- Earmuffs. - Nice.

1337
01:02:46,156 --> 01:02:47,325
Gloves and earmuffs.

1338
01:02:47,326 --> 01:02:48,326
(The parents of daughters are satisfied with the present.)

1339
01:02:48,327 --> 01:02:49,766
That's pretty nice.

1340
01:02:50,936 --> 01:02:51,965
(Satisfied)

1341
01:02:51,966 --> 01:02:53,366
You're smart.

1342
01:02:53,696 --> 01:02:55,306
He was smart about it.

1343
01:02:55,866 --> 01:02:57,975
I thought my date would like it...

1344
01:02:57,976 --> 01:02:59,906
when she got it.

1345
01:03:00,106 --> 01:03:04,245
He might've used this method...

1346
01:03:04,246 --> 01:03:07,046
when he tried to appeal to women when he was my age.

1347
01:03:09,216 --> 01:03:10,885
- Even your son knows. - Did you do that?

1348
01:03:10,886 --> 01:03:12,916
I didn't do that.

1349
01:03:13,256 --> 01:03:15,085
- It's quite cold there. - Yes.

1350
01:03:15,086 --> 01:03:18,895
So I thought gloves and earmuffs would be nice.

1351
01:03:18,896 --> 01:03:20,295
You wanted your son to look good in their eyes.

1352
01:03:20,296 --> 01:03:22,626
Yes. But it's not about the physical warmness.

1353
01:03:22,766 --> 01:03:24,835
It's about how warm he is.

1354
01:03:24,836 --> 01:03:25,935
- Mentally. - How warm-hearted he is.

1355
01:03:25,936 --> 01:03:27,336
Convey your warm-heartedness.

1356
01:03:27,906 --> 01:03:29,506
Say something like that to your date.

1357
01:03:30,206 --> 01:03:32,175
That's what I'm hoping for.

1358
01:03:32,176 --> 01:03:33,475
Out of the three fathers,

1359
01:03:33,476 --> 01:03:35,806
that's the most likable present.

1360
01:03:36,006 --> 01:03:38,675
- Yes. - And they'll play the music.

1361
01:03:38,676 --> 01:03:39,676
(Satisfied)

1362
01:03:40,046 --> 01:03:42,646
(Hee Dong is checking his present box.)

1363
01:03:43,016 --> 01:03:46,816
(What date present did Tae Woong prepare?)

1364
01:03:46,986 --> 01:03:48,525
It was a necklace.

1365
01:03:48,526 --> 01:03:51,126
(A bear-shaped necklace)

1366
01:03:51,396 --> 01:03:53,095
(A necklace?)

1367
01:03:53,096 --> 01:03:55,025
- A necklace? - That's worldly.

1368
01:03:55,026 --> 01:03:56,225
(It's expensive.)

1369
01:03:56,226 --> 01:03:57,495
This is...

1370
01:03:57,496 --> 01:03:58,735
It's worldly.

1371
01:03:58,736 --> 01:04:00,335
It sure sets him apart.

1372
01:04:00,336 --> 01:04:01,336
The presents are getting more and more impactful.

1373
01:04:01,337 --> 01:04:02,805
- That's a strong one. - Yes.

1374
01:04:02,806 --> 01:04:05,175
Actually, very few ladies...

1375
01:04:05,176 --> 01:04:07,745
dislike accessories.

1376
01:04:07,746 --> 01:04:08,946
- That's true. - So...

1377
01:04:09,346 --> 01:04:12,215
I thought this could work well.

1378
01:04:12,216 --> 01:04:14,145
The poetry book is too weak.

1379
01:04:14,146 --> 01:04:16,116
The poetry book will be pushed aside.

1380
01:04:16,646 --> 01:04:19,986
When I saw it, I thought, "Dad really prepared this?"

1381
01:04:20,316 --> 01:04:23,156
I couldn't believe it.

1382
01:04:23,456 --> 01:04:26,555
I thought my dad was wittier...

1383
01:04:26,556 --> 01:04:27,696
than I took him to be.

1384
01:04:28,696 --> 01:04:30,226
I think it's a really good present.

1385
01:04:30,596 --> 01:04:32,065
My gosh.

1386
01:04:32,066 --> 01:04:36,166
(Which son will deliver the date present first?)

1387
01:04:36,836 --> 01:04:38,036
Have the rest done it already?

1388
01:04:38,336 --> 01:04:40,806
No, none of them are awake yet.

1389
01:04:40,846 --> 01:04:41,846
You should go quickly.

1390
01:04:41,847 --> 01:04:43,046
- Why isn't he doing it? - Why isn't he doing it?

1391
01:04:44,216 --> 01:04:45,745
I don't think anyone woke up.

1392
01:04:45,746 --> 01:04:47,786
- I think so too. - Right?

1393
01:04:48,016 --> 01:04:50,786
(They're waiting because they think the girls are still sleeping.)

1394
01:04:51,356 --> 01:04:54,186
I thought they could still be sleeping.

1395
01:04:54,786 --> 01:04:57,926
It felt a bit uncomfortable to be the first to do it.

1396
01:04:59,456 --> 01:05:01,795
More than worrying about...

1397
01:05:01,796 --> 01:05:04,436
the other guys asking them out first,

1398
01:05:04,696 --> 01:05:08,005
I didn't know what to say when giving them the present,

1399
01:05:08,006 --> 01:05:09,306
so I took some time to think about it.

1400
01:05:10,576 --> 01:05:13,106
(The sons are staying in the room due to their own reasons.)

1401
01:05:13,336 --> 01:05:15,206
They're so frustrating.

1402
01:05:16,606 --> 01:05:19,216
What is he doing? Goodness.

1403
01:05:19,376 --> 01:05:22,246
It was first-come first-served, so I should ask her out quickly.

1404
01:05:22,716 --> 01:05:26,285
But I thought she would prefer it if I looked decent.

1405
01:05:26,286 --> 01:05:27,355
So I washed quickly.

1406
01:05:27,356 --> 01:05:29,055
But it'll be too late once you wash up.

1407
01:05:29,056 --> 01:05:30,255
- Exactly. - Yes.

1408
01:05:30,256 --> 01:05:32,425
I'm so frustrated. What is he doing?

1409
01:05:32,426 --> 01:05:34,226
He's driving me insane.

1410
01:05:35,296 --> 01:05:38,666
(While the sons are deep in thought,)

1411
01:05:38,936 --> 01:05:42,836
(the girls have been long awake and are waiting for them.)

1412
01:05:42,966 --> 01:05:44,035
Did you ask anyone out?

1413
01:05:44,036 --> 01:05:45,176
- Not yet. - I see.

1414
01:05:45,606 --> 01:05:46,775
(Meanwhile, Yoon Hoo finishes washing.)

1415
01:05:46,776 --> 01:05:48,246
(Glancing)

1416
01:05:48,376 --> 01:05:49,706
- You all haven't? - No.

1417
01:05:55,616 --> 01:05:58,355
(Yoon Hoo runs without looking back.)

1418
01:05:58,356 --> 01:06:00,185
- Look at him. - He's running.

1419
01:06:00,186 --> 01:06:03,126
- Way to go, son! - Yoon Hoo.

1420
01:06:03,256 --> 01:06:04,355
Go!

1421
01:06:04,356 --> 01:06:06,226
(This is it.)

1422
01:06:06,496 --> 01:06:08,225
I haven't even dried my hair yet.

1423
01:06:08,226 --> 01:06:11,165
But since it's first-come first-served,

1424
01:06:11,166 --> 01:06:13,166
I thought I should hurry.

1425
01:06:14,266 --> 01:06:15,735
(Turning around)

1426
01:06:15,736 --> 01:06:16,905
- Dry your hair. - What?

1427
01:06:16,906 --> 01:06:20,135
That's it! Just say it! Spit it out!

1428
01:06:20,136 --> 01:06:21,675
Who is it, Hoo?

1429
01:06:21,676 --> 01:06:23,046
(Who is in Yoon Hoo's mind?)

1430
01:06:23,507 --> 01:06:25,076
I haven't even dried my hair yet.

1431
01:06:25,077 --> 01:06:28,076
But since it's first-come first-served,

1432
01:06:28,077 --> 01:06:30,177
I thought I should hurry.

1433
01:06:31,077 --> 01:06:32,746
(Turning around)

1434
01:06:32,747 --> 01:06:33,876
- Dry your hair. - What?

1435
01:06:33,877 --> 01:06:37,086
That's it! Just say it! Spit it out!

1436
01:06:37,087 --> 01:06:39,287
Who is it, Hoo?

1437
01:06:39,887 --> 01:06:41,426
(Which daughter will Hoo ask out?)

1438
01:06:41,427 --> 01:06:42,487
Hello.

1439
01:06:43,557 --> 01:06:44,657
Yu Bin, can I have a moment with you?

1440
01:06:45,757 --> 01:06:47,666
- Can you stir it once? - I'll keep an eye on it.

1441
01:06:47,667 --> 01:06:50,196
(Yoon Hoo chooses Yu Bin.)

1442
01:06:50,197 --> 01:06:52,696
- That's it! - He called Yu Bin.

1443
01:06:52,697 --> 01:06:54,466
That's it!

1444
01:06:54,467 --> 01:06:56,766
- That's my son. - He's so straightforward.

1445
01:06:56,767 --> 01:06:59,106
Nice. That's how a man should be.

1446
01:06:59,107 --> 01:07:00,306
- That's cheating. - Yes.

1447
01:07:00,307 --> 01:07:01,507
- A man... - He's disqualified.

1448
01:07:05,847 --> 01:07:07,647
- Yes? What... - Please go inside.

1449
01:07:09,247 --> 01:07:11,356
Me? Why...

1450
01:07:11,357 --> 01:07:12,587
Why am I in here?

1451
01:07:13,787 --> 01:07:15,557
- So nobody can snatch you away. - I see.

1452
01:07:15,727 --> 01:07:17,756
- "So nobody can snatch you away." - "So nobody can snatch you away."

1453
01:07:17,757 --> 01:07:20,126
(What he said makes her dad happy.)

1454
01:07:20,127 --> 01:07:21,366
That's it!

1455
01:07:21,367 --> 01:07:23,197
- That's cheating! - What a nice thing to say.

1456
01:07:23,327 --> 01:07:25,466
Women are deeply moved...

1457
01:07:25,467 --> 01:07:28,837
- when they hear stuff like this. - Of course.

1458
01:07:29,007 --> 01:07:31,907
- Yu Bin is moved now. - Yes, she is.

1459
01:07:35,847 --> 01:07:38,776
(In a rush, he wears Jae Hyuk's jacket.)

1460
01:07:38,777 --> 01:07:39,917
- Jae Hyuk's jacket? - What?

1461
01:07:40,317 --> 01:07:41,517
What is he doing?

1462
01:07:41,687 --> 01:07:43,717
- It isn't even his. - What is he doing?

1463
01:07:44,287 --> 01:07:46,157
(Knocking)

1464
01:07:50,527 --> 01:07:52,097
- Hello. - Hello.

1465
01:07:52,627 --> 01:07:55,327
They're my presents for you.

1466
01:07:55,867 --> 01:07:57,667
My gosh.

1467
01:07:57,767 --> 01:07:58,797
What are these for?

1468
01:07:59,567 --> 01:08:00,736
Go on a date with me.

1469
01:08:00,737 --> 01:08:02,336
Really? Sure.

1470
01:08:02,337 --> 01:08:03,436
Go on a date with me.

1471
01:08:03,437 --> 01:08:05,607
Really? Sure, I'd like that.

1472
01:08:05,837 --> 01:08:06,977
Nobody asked you out yet, right?

1473
01:08:07,437 --> 01:08:08,447
No.

1474
01:08:08,747 --> 01:08:10,246
- Is this first-come first-served? - That's right.

1475
01:08:10,247 --> 01:08:12,816
- I see. Thank you. - No problem.

1476
01:08:12,817 --> 01:08:15,117
(Yu Bin is the first to be asked out by Yoon Hoo.)

1477
01:08:16,687 --> 01:08:20,787
The presents would keep me warm during the date,

1478
01:08:20,857 --> 01:08:22,057
so I liked it.

1479
01:08:22,327 --> 01:08:23,627
I felt very good.

1480
01:08:23,727 --> 01:08:25,997
She must be on cloud nine.

1481
01:08:26,397 --> 01:08:29,366
(Those left now are Hee Dong, Jae Seung,)

1482
01:08:29,367 --> 01:08:31,767
(and Jae Hyuk.)

1483
01:08:32,497 --> 01:08:34,266
- I think it's almost done. - Yes.

1484
01:08:34,267 --> 01:08:35,307
(Eun Byul and Si Woo are waiting for the guys to ask them out.)

1485
01:08:37,437 --> 01:08:38,936
This is bad.

1486
01:08:38,937 --> 01:08:41,407
We should be saying that. This is bad.

1487
01:08:42,677 --> 01:08:45,677
(Checking his face)

1488
01:08:47,247 --> 01:08:52,057
(After looking in the mirror, Jae Seung finally gets going.)

1489
01:08:52,887 --> 01:08:56,457
I have one person in mind.

1490
01:09:00,827 --> 01:09:02,426
Excuse me, Si Woo. Could I...

1491
01:09:02,427 --> 01:09:03,966
- speak with you for a moment? - Okay.

1492
01:09:03,967 --> 01:09:07,907
(The girl on Jae Seung's mind is Si Woo.)

1493
01:09:09,167 --> 01:09:10,537
Si Woo.

1494
01:09:11,377 --> 01:09:13,207
He's ever so consistent.

1495
01:09:13,837 --> 01:09:15,576
He wavered for a moment,

1496
01:09:15,577 --> 01:09:17,577
but he went back to being consistent.

1497
01:09:18,117 --> 01:09:19,217
(Wiping his nose)

1498
01:09:19,877 --> 01:09:21,887
- Please wait for a while. - Okay.

1499
01:09:26,157 --> 01:09:29,287
(He takes the poetry book with a fluttering heart.)

1500
01:09:29,557 --> 01:09:30,587
Well...

1501
01:09:31,657 --> 01:09:35,367
I'd like to ask you out on a date.

1502
01:09:35,727 --> 01:09:37,166
- Here. - Thank you.

1503
01:09:37,167 --> 01:09:39,767
(Jae Seung asks Si Woo out as he gives her the poetry book.)

1504
01:09:40,537 --> 01:09:43,937
(Feeling embarrassed, he runs away quickly.)

1505
01:09:44,407 --> 01:09:47,077
(Did you like Jae Seung's present?)

1506
01:09:47,277 --> 01:09:49,876
Jae Seung came to me first...

1507
01:09:49,877 --> 01:09:51,476
and gave me...

1508
01:09:51,477 --> 01:09:53,847
a collection of poems.

1509
01:09:54,217 --> 01:09:57,186
- Will she like it? - Does Si Woo like poetry?

1510
01:09:57,187 --> 01:09:58,317
Does she like it?

1511
01:09:58,817 --> 01:10:02,486
I really like the poem "Grass Flower..."

1512
01:10:02,487 --> 01:10:04,256
and I read it often.

1513
01:10:04,257 --> 01:10:08,297
I thought, "Is this coincidence?"

1514
01:10:09,667 --> 01:10:11,367
His dad chose it.

1515
01:10:11,767 --> 01:10:13,766
- And it worked. - She likes it.

1516
01:10:13,767 --> 01:10:15,737
(The poetry book captures Si Woo's heart.)

1517
01:10:16,137 --> 01:10:17,206
(Why did you ask Si Woo out on a date?)

1518
01:10:17,207 --> 01:10:20,636
I remember asking her...

1519
01:10:20,637 --> 01:10:23,177
if she would be okay with going on a date with me.

1520
01:10:23,507 --> 01:10:25,477
(During their first meeting)

1521
01:10:25,677 --> 01:10:27,477
I like taking pictures.

1522
01:10:27,817 --> 01:10:31,857
(They both like taking pictures.)

1523
01:10:32,587 --> 01:10:33,957
During the Attraction Selection,

1524
01:10:34,527 --> 01:10:36,086
I think the message I got was,

1525
01:10:36,087 --> 01:10:38,557
"Let's go to a scenic spot and take pictures together."

1526
01:10:38,727 --> 01:10:40,857
I thought that was from Si Woo.

1527
01:10:41,127 --> 01:10:42,666
It'd be nice to go on a date with her...

1528
01:10:42,667 --> 01:10:44,196
to a place with a nice view.

1529
01:10:44,197 --> 01:10:46,937
That's why he asked Si Woo out.

1530
01:10:47,637 --> 01:10:50,137
But Eun Byul sent that text.

1531
01:10:51,237 --> 01:10:52,906
The date will be tough.

1532
01:10:52,907 --> 01:10:54,177
He thought long and hard.

1533
01:10:54,337 --> 01:10:57,106
I think Jae Seung is a fool.

1534
01:10:57,107 --> 01:10:58,777
He's so dense.

1535
01:10:59,147 --> 01:11:01,086
- That can't be true. - He's so dense.

1536
01:11:01,087 --> 01:11:03,087
He's unaware of my daughter's feelings.

1537
01:11:03,647 --> 01:11:06,157
- The date will be rough. - Why?

1538
01:11:06,317 --> 01:11:09,556
Jae Seung thinks Si Woo sent him the text.

1539
01:11:09,557 --> 01:11:11,596
- Yes. - But once the truth comes out...

1540
01:11:11,597 --> 01:11:12,627
Yes.

1541
01:11:12,797 --> 01:11:13,956
It'll be...

1542
01:11:13,957 --> 01:11:15,966
They can become closer before they find out the truth.

1543
01:11:15,967 --> 01:11:17,837
- Yes. - You never know how it'll turn out.

1544
01:11:17,967 --> 01:11:22,007
(Meanwhile, Eun Byul is left alone in the kitchen.)

1545
01:11:22,467 --> 01:11:26,577
I voted for Jae Seung.

1546
01:11:26,807 --> 01:11:29,006
So I hoped...

1547
01:11:29,007 --> 01:11:32,746
to go on a 1-on-1 date with Jae Seung.

1548
01:11:32,747 --> 01:11:33,977
Oh, dear.

1549
01:11:34,017 --> 01:11:36,117
(Upset)

1550
01:11:38,787 --> 01:11:41,257
It's a pity,

1551
01:11:41,687 --> 01:11:44,957
but I think I have a lot of opportunities to talk with him.

1552
01:11:48,097 --> 01:11:49,227
Did you ask someone out?

1553
01:11:49,467 --> 01:11:50,666
- I did. - You did?

1554
01:11:50,667 --> 01:11:52,467
- I'll go now. - Do your best.

1555
01:11:53,297 --> 01:11:55,636
Are we supposed to go one by one...

1556
01:11:55,637 --> 01:11:57,207
when it's first-come first-served?

1557
01:11:58,777 --> 01:12:00,636
Shouldn't we fight to go first?

1558
01:12:00,637 --> 01:12:02,077
- That's right. - That's right.

1559
